cpu      = cpu time in seconds executing 
elapsed  = elapsed time in seconds executing
disk     = number of physical reads of buffers from disk

WITH OBJECT AS ( SELECT /*+ MATERIALIZE */ OBJECT_OWNER OWNER, OBJECT_NAME 
  NAME FROM GV$SQL_PLAN WHERE INST_ID IN (SELECT INST_ID FROM GV$INSTANCE) 
  AND SQL_ID = :B1 AND OBJECT_OWNER IS NOT NULL AND OBJECT_NAME IS NOT NULL 
  UNION SELECT OBJECT_OWNER OWNER, OBJECT_NAME NAME FROM DBA_HIST_SQL_PLAN 
  WHERE :B3 = 'Y' AND DBID = :B2 AND SQL_ID = :B1 AND OBJECT_OWNER IS NOT 
  NULL AND OBJECT_NAME IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT CASE H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 
  THEN 'SYS' ELSE O.OWNER END OWNER, CASE H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 THEN 'UNDO' 
  ELSE O.OBJECT_NAME END NAME FROM GV$ACTIVE_SESSION_HISTORY H, DBA_OBJECTS O 
  WHERE :B3 = 'Y' AND H.SQL_ID = :B1 AND H.CURRENT_OBJ# >= 0 AND 
  O.OBJECT_ID(+) = H.CURRENT_OBJ# UNION SELECT /*+
               
  FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn)
               
  FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash)
               
  FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)
               
  USE_HASH(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn 
  h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)
   
              FULL(h.sn)
               FULL(h.ash)
               FULL(h.evt)
  
               USE_HASH(h.sn h.ash h.evt)
               */ CASE 
  H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 THEN 'SYS' ELSE O.OWNER END OWNER, CASE 
  H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 THEN 'UNDO' ELSE O.OBJECT_NAME END NAME FROM 
  DBA_HIST_ACTIVE_SESS_HISTORY H, DBA_OBJECTS O WHERE :B3 = 'Y' AND H.DBID = 
  :B2 AND H.SQL_ID = :B1 AND H.CURRENT_OBJ# >= 0 AND O.OBJECT_ID(+) = 
  H.CURRENT_OBJ# ) SELECT 'TABLE', T.OWNER, T.TABLE_NAME FROM 
  DBA_TAB_STATISTICS T, OBJECT O WHERE T.OWNER = O.OWNER AND T.TABLE_NAME = 
  O.NAME UNION SELECT 'TABLE', I.TABLE_OWNER, I.TABLE_NAME FROM DBA_INDEXES I,
   OBJECT O WHERE I.OWNER = O.OWNER AND I.INDEX_NAME = O.NAME

WITH RANKED_SQL AS ( SELECT /*+  DYNAMIC_SAMPLING(4)   FULL(h.ash) FULL(h.evt)

  FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash) 
  FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)

  h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)  
  */ CON_ID, DBID, SQL_ID, MAX(USER_ID) USER_ID, MAX(MODULE) MODULE, 
  ROUND(COUNT(*) / 360, 6) DB_TIME_HRS, ROUND(SUM(CASE SESSION_STATE WHEN 'ON 
  CPU' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / 360, 6) CPU_TIME_HRS, ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN 
  SESSION_STATE = 'WAITING' AND WAIT_CLASS IN ('User I/O', 'System I/O') THEN 
  1 ELSE 0 END) / 360, 6) IO_TIME_HRS, ROW_NUMBER () OVER (ORDER BY COUNT(*) 
  DESC) RANK_NUM FROM DBA_HIST_ACTIVE_SESS_HISTORY H WHERE SQL_ID IS NOT NULL 
  AND SNAP_ID BETWEEN 3473 AND 4962 AND DBID = 2109323688 AND '' IS NULL 
  GROUP BY CON_ID, DBID, SQL_ID HAVING COUNT(*) > 60 ), TOP_SQL AS ( SELECT 
  /*+  MATERIALIZE NO_MERGE  7b.1045 */ R.CON_ID, R.SQL_ID, 
  TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(R.DB_TIME_HRS, 2), '99990.00')) DB_TIME_HRS, 
  TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(R.CPU_TIME_HRS, 2), '99990.00')) CPU_TIME_HRS, 
  TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(R.IO_TIME_HRS, 2), '99990.00')) IO_TIME_HRS, R.RANK_NUM, 
  NVL((SELECT A.NAME FROM AUDIT_ACTIONS A WHERE A.ACTION = H.COMMAND_TYPE), 
  TO_CHAR(H.COMMAND_TYPE)) COMMAND_TYPE, NVL((SELECT U.USERNAME FROM 
  DBA_USERS U WHERE U.USER_ID = R.USER_ID), TO_CHAR(R.USER_ID)) USERNAME, 
  R.MODULE, CASE WHEN H.SQL_TEXT IS NULL THEN 'unknown' ELSE 
  REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(DBMS_LOB.SUBSTR(H.SQL_TEXT, 1000), CHR(10),

  END SQL_TEXT_1000 FROM RANKED_SQL R, DBA_HIST_SQLTEXT H WHERE R.RANK_NUM <= 
  16 AND H.CON_ID(+) = R.CON_ID AND H.DBID(+) = R.DBID AND H.SQL_ID(+) = 
  R.SQL_ID ), NOT_SHARED AS ( SELECT /*+ 7b.1045 */ CON_ID, SQL_ID, COUNT(*) 
  CHILD_CURSORS, RANK() OVER (ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC NULLS LAST) AS SQL_RANK 
  FROM GV$SQL_SHARED_CURSOR WHERE SQL_ID NOT IN (SELECT SQL_ID FROM TOP_SQL) 
  GROUP BY CON_ID, SQL_ID HAVING COUNT(*) > 100 ), TOP_NOT_SHARED AS ( SELECT 
  /*+  MATERIALIZE NO_MERGE  7b.1045 */ DISTINCT NS.SQL_RANK,

  AS ( SELECT /*+ FULL(ts) FULL(ns) USE_HASH(ts ns h)  MATERIALIZE NO_MERGE

SELECT i.index_owner||'.'||i.index_name||' '||c.column_name index_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_ind_columns i,
       dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('SYS','USER$'),('THH_ADDRESS','T_CITYOR_TOWN'),('THH_ADDRESS','T_CNTY'),('THH_C4C','A_RSPE'),('THH_C4C','A_RSPECHCS'),('THH_C4C','A_TAKNASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','CERME_CONFIG'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATADEF'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAENTRY'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUE'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUEDEF'),('THH_C4C','INSTRUCTION_CARD_ASSOC'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_CAREPLAN'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_CAREPLAN_MEMBDGISB'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','OPS_ACTIVITY_INCIDENT'),('THH_C4C','OPS_RELATED_DATA'),('THH_C4C','T_ALRT'),('THH_C4C','T_APBL'),('THH_C4C','T_ASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TMPT_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_BENSPKG'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_GOALCP_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_MEMBDGISBASE_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_TODO_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CHCE'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_BASEBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_CTCS'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCT'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCTDTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_COORDINATION_OF_BENEFITS'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDS'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDSMETADAT'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL_ITEM'),('THH_C4C','T_DGIS'),('THH_C4C','T_DGIS_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_EDNLCNTTDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_ENNS'),('THH_C4C','T_FIL'),('THH_C4C','T_FRDSAND_FMLYLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_FRMA'),('THH_C4C','T_FRM_CELLTXT'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TODO_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_GPI_CODE'),('THH_C4C','T_ICMGFAX'),('THH_C4C','T_INSCPRSRGRP'),('THH_C4C','T_LNGSLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_LTR_TMPT'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCLCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE_GOALCP_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE_OUTCOME_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_NOTE'),('THH_C4C','T_NTCE'),('THH_C4C','T_ORG_CHRTITEMPRSS'),('THH_C4C','T_OTHER_INSURANCE'),('THH_C4C','T_OUTCOME'),('THH_C4C','T_PAYRDGISSCTY'),('THH_C4C','T_PAYRROLS'),('THH_C4C','T_PHI'),('THH_C4C','T_PRMR'),('THH_C4C','T_PRODCAT'),('THH_C4C','T_PROVIDER_CHOICE'),('THH_C4C','T_PROVIDER_CHOICE_ROLE_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_PRSC'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRASTN'),('THH_C4C','T_QTN'),('THH_C4C','T_REVWHEAD'),('THH_C4C','T_REVWREC'),('THH_C4C','T_RSPE'),('THH_C4C','T_RSPECHCS'),('THH_C4C','T_SENTTSK'),('THH_C4C','T_SYTMSTNGDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_TAKNASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_TIM_OFF_REQT'),('THH_C4C','T_TNFRREC'),('THH_C4C','T_TODO'),('THH_C4C','T_TODO_ASSMTCC_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_TODO_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_TODO_NOTE_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_TODO_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_TSK_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_TSK_TMPTAMTS'),('THH_C4C','T_TSK_TMPTEDNLCNNS'),('THH_C4C','T_UM_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_ADD'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_CNCTINFOPAYRDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_PREFERENCES'))
   AND c.owner = i.table_owner
   AND c.table_name = i.table_name
   AND c.column_name = i.column_name
 ORDER BY
       i.index_owner,
       i.index_name,
       i.column_position

SELECT i.index_owner||'.'||i.index_name||' '||c.column_name index_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_ind_columns i,
       dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('SYS','USER$'),('SYS','WRM$_SNAPSHOT_DETAILS'),('THH_ADDRESS','T_CITYOR_TOWN'),('THH_C4C','A_RSPECHCS'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAENTRY'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUE'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_CAREPLAN_MEMBDGISB'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','OPS_ACTIVITY_INCIDENT'),('THH_C4C','T_ALRT'),('THH_C4C','T_ASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TMPT_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_BENSPKG'),('THH_C4C','T_BEN_FIL'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_GOALCP_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_MEMBDGISBASE_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_TODO_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_BASEBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_CTCS'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_PRJ_PERS'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCT'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCTDTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_COORDINATION_OF_BENEFITS'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDS'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDSMETADAT'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL_ITEM'),('THH_C4C','T_DGIS'),('THH_C4C','T_DRUGCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_EDNLCNTTDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_ENNS'),('THH_C4C','T_FIL'),('THH_C4C','T_FRDSAND_FMLYLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_FRMA'),('THH_C4C','T_FRM_CELLTXT'),('THH_C4C','T_FRM_TTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TMP_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TODO_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_INSCPRSRGRP'),('THH_C4C','T_LNGSLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_LTR_TMPT'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCLCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE_GOALCP_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE_OUTCOME_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_NOTE'),('THH_C4C','T_NTCE'),('THH_C4C','T_OTHER_INSURANCE'),('THH_C4C','T_OUTCOME'),('THH_C4C','T_PAYRDGISSCTY'),('THH_C4C','T_PAYRROLS'),('THH_C4C','T_PHI'),('THH_C4C','T_PRMR'),('THH_C4C','T_PRODCAT'),('THH_C4C','T_PROVIDER_CHOICE'),('THH_C4C','T_PROVIDER_CHOICE_ROLE_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_PRSC'),('THH_C4C','T_QTN'),('THH_C4C','T_REVWHEAD'),('THH_C4C','T_REVWREC'),('THH_C4C','T_RSPE'),('THH_C4C','T_RSPECHCS'),('THH_C4C','T_SENTTSK'),('THH_C4C','T_TAKNASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_TNFRREC'),('THH_C4C','T_TODO'),('THH_C4C','T_TODO_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_TODO_NOTE_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_TODO_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_TSK_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_TSK_TMPTAMTS'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_ADD'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_PREFERENCES'),('THH_C4C','T_WKFWTSK'))
   AND c.owner = i.table_owner
   AND c.table_name = i.table_name
   AND c.column_name = i.column_name
 ORDER BY
       i.index_owner,
       i.index_name,
       i.column_position

SELECT i.index_owner||'.'||i.index_name||' '||c.column_name index_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_ind_columns i,
       dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('SYS','TRG_LOGON'),('SYS','USER$'),('SYS','WRM$_SNAPSHOT_DETAILS'),('THH_ADDRESS','T_CITYOR_TOWN'),('THH_C4C','A_FIL'),('THH_C4C','A_RSPE'),('THH_C4C','A_RSPECHCS'),('THH_C4C','A_TAKNASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','A_USR'),('THH_C4C','CERME_CONFIG'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAENTRY'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUE'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUEDEF'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUE_AUDIT'),('THH_C4C','EDCONTENTKEYS'),('THH_C4C','FACT_TMPT_VTB'),('THH_C4C','INSTRUCTION_CARD'),('THH_C4C','INSTRUCTION_CARD_ASSOC'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_CAREPLAN'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_CAREPLAN_MEMBDGISB'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','OPS_ACTIVITY_INCIDENT'),('THH_C4C','OPS_RELATED_DATA'),('THH_C4C','T_ALRT'),('THH_C4C','T_APBL'),('THH_C4C','T_ASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_ASMTLTR_HEDS'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TMPT_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_BENSPKG'),('THH_C4C','T_BEN_FIL'),('THH_C4C','T_BLR_PLT'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_GOALCP_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_MEMBDGISBASE_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_TODO_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CHCE'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_BASEBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_CTCS'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_PRJ_PERS'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCT'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCTDTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_COORDINATION_OF_BENEFITS'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDS'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDSMETADAT'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL_ITEM'),('THH_C4C','T_DGIS'),('THH_C4C','T_DGIS_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_DRUGCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_EDNLCNTTDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_ENNS'),('THH_C4C','T_FIL'),('THH_C4C','T_FRDSAND_FMLYLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_FRMA'),('THH_C4C','T_FRM_CELLTXT'),('THH_C4C','T_FRM_TTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TMP_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TODO_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_ICMGFAX'),('THH_C4C','T_INSCPRSRGRP'),('THH_C4C','T_LNGSLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_LTR_TMPT'),('THH_C4C','T_LTR_TMPTEDNLCNNS'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCLCLM'),('THH_C        i.index_owner,
       i.index_name,
       i.column_position

********************************************************************************

WITH
events AS (
SELECT /*+ MATERIALIZE */
       h.sql_plan_hash_value plan_hash_value,
       NVL(h.sql_plan_line_id, 0) line_id_ff,
       SUBSTR(h.sql_plan_operation||' '||h.sql_plan_options, 1, 50) operation_ff,
       CASE h.session_state WHEN 'ON CPU' THEN -1 ELSE h.current_obj# END current_obj#,
       CASE h.session_state WHEN 'ON CPU' THEN h.session_state ELSE h.wait_class||' "'||h.event||'"' END timed_event,
       COUNT(*) samples
  FROM gv$active_session_history h
 WHERE :license = 'Y'
   AND sql_id = :sql_id
 GROUP BY
       h.sql_plan_hash_value,
       h.sql_plan_line_id,
       h.sql_plan_operation,
       h.sql_plan_options,
       CASE h.session_state WHEN 'ON CPU' THEN -1 ELSE h.current_obj# END,
       CASE h.session_state WHEN 'ON CPU' THEN h.session_state ELSE h.wait_class||' "'||h.event||'"' END
 ORDER BY
       6 DESC
),
total AS (
SELECT SUM(samples) samples,
       SUM(CASE WHEN ROWNUM > 20 THEN samples ELSE 0 END) others
  FROM events
)
SELECT e.samples samples_ff,
       ROUND(100 * e.samples / t.samples, 1) percent_ff,
       e.plan_hash_value,
       e.line_id_ff,
       e.operation_ff,
       SUBSTR(e.current_obj#||' '||TRIM(
       (SELECT CASE e.current_obj# WHEN 0 THEN ' UNDO' ELSE ' '||o.owner||'.'||o.object_name||' ('||o.object_type||')' END
          FROM dba_objects o WHERE o.object_id(+) = e.current_obj# AND ROWNUM = 1)
       ), 1, 60) current_object_ff,
       e.timed_event timed_event_ff
  FROM events e,
       total t
 WHERE ROWNUM <= 20
   AND ROUND(100 * e.samples / t.samples, 1) > 0.1
 UNION ALL
SELECT others samples_ff,
       ROUND(100 * others / samples, 1) percent_ff,
       TO_NUMBER(NULL) plan_hash_value,
       TO_NUMBER(NULL) id,
       NULL operation_ff,
       NULL current_object_ff,
       'Others' timed_event_ff
  FROM total
 WHERE others > 0
   AND ROUND(100 * others / samples, 1) > 0.1

WITH
events AS (
SELECT /*+ MATERIALIZE */
       h.sql_plan_hash_value plan_hash_value,
       NVL(h.sql_plan_line_id, 0) line_id_ff,
       SUBSTR(h.sql_plan_operation||' '||h.sql_plan_options, 1, 50) operation_ff,
       CASE h.session_state WHEN 'ON CPU' THEN h.session_state ELSE h.wait_class||' "'||h.event||'"' END timed_event,
       COUNT(*) samples
  FROM gv$active_session_history h
 WHERE :license = 'Y'
   AND sql_id = :sql_id
 GROUP BY
       h.sql_plan_hash_value,
       h.sql_plan_line_id,
       h.sql_plan_operation,
       h.sql_plan_options,
       CASE h.session_state WHEN 'ON CPU' THEN h.session_state ELSE h.wait_class||' "'||h.event||'"' END
 ORDER BY
       5 DESC
),
total AS (
SELECT SUM(samples) samples,
       SUM(CASE WHEN ROWNUM > 15 THEN samples ELSE 0 END) others
  FROM events
)
SELECT e.samples samples_ff,
       ROUND(100 * e.samples / t.samples, 1) percent_ff,
       e.plan_hash_value,
       e.line_id_ff,
       e.operation_ff,
       e.timed_event timed_event_ff
  FROM events e,
       total t
 WHERE ROWNUM <= 15
   AND ROUND(100 * e.samples / t.samples, 1) > 0.1
 UNION ALL
SELECT others samples_ff,
       ROUND(100 * others / samples, 1) percent_ff,
       TO_NUMBER(NULL) plan_hash_value,
       TO_NUMBER(NULL) id,
       NULL operation_ff,
       'Others' timed_event_ff
  FROM total
 WHERE others > 0
   AND ROUND(100 * others / samples, 1) > 0.1

WITH
events AS (
SELECT /*+ MATERIALIZE */
       CASE h.session_state WHEN 'ON CPU' THEN h.session_state ELSE h.wait_class||' "'||h.event||'"' END timed_event,
       COUNT(*) samples
  FROM gv$active_session_history h
 WHERE :license = 'Y'
   AND sql_id = :sql_id
 GROUP BY
       CASE h.session_state WHEN 'ON CPU' THEN h.session_state ELSE h.wait_class||' "'||h.event||'"' END
 ORDER BY
       2 DESC
),
total AS (
SELECT SUM(samples) samples,
       SUM(CASE WHEN ROWNUM > 10 THEN samples ELSE 0 END) others
  FROM events
)
SELECT e.samples samples_ff,
       ROUND(100 * e.samples / t.samples, 1) percent_ff,
       e.timed_event timed_event_ff
  FROM events e,
       total t
 WHERE ROWNUM <= 10
   AND ROUND(100 * e.samples / t.samples, 1) > 0.1
 UNION ALL
SELECT others samples_ff,
       ROUND(100 * others / samples, 1) percent_ff,
       'Others' timed_event_ff
  FROM total
 WHERE others > 0
   AND ROUND(100 * others / samples, 1) > 0.1

WITH
events AS (
SELECT /*+
       FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn)
       FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash)
       FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)
       USE_HASH(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)
       FULL(h.sn)
       FULL(h.ash)
       FULL(h.evt)
       USE_HASH(h.sn h.ash h.evt)
       */
       h.sql_plan_hash_value plan_hash_value,
       NVL(h.sql_plan_line_id, 0) line_id_ff,
       SUBSTR(h.sql_plan_operation||' '||h.sql_plan_options, 1, 50) operation_ff,
       CASE h.session_state WHEN 'ON CPU' THEN -1 ELSE h.current_obj# END current_obj#,
       CASE h.session_state WHEN 'ON CPU' THEN h.session_state ELSE h.wait_class||' "'||h.event||'"' END timed_event,
       COUNT(*) samples
  FROM dba_hist_active_sess_history h
 WHERE :license = 'Y'
   AND h.dbid = :dbid
   AND h.sql_id = :sql_id
   AND h.snap_id BETWEEN 3483 AND 4973
 GROUP BY
       h.sql_plan_hash_value,
       h.sql_plan_line_id,
       h.sql_plan_operation,
       h.sql_plan_options,
       CASE h.session_state WHEN 'ON CPU' THEN -1 ELSE h.current_obj# END,
       CASE h.session_state WHEN 'ON CPU' THEN h.session_state ELSE h.wait_class||' "'||h.event||'"' END
 ORDER BY
       6 DESC
),
total AS (
SELECT SUM(samples) samples,
       SUM(CASE WHEN ROWNUM > 20 THEN samples ELSE 0 END) others
  FROM events
)
SELECT e.samples samples_ff,
       ROUND(100 * e.samples / t.samples, 1) percent_ff,
       e.plan_hash_value,
       e.line_id_ff,
       e.operation_ff,
       SUBSTR(e.current_obj#||' '||TRIM(
       (SELECT CASE e.current_obj# WHEN 0 THEN ' UNDO' ELSE ' '||o.owner||'.'||o.object_name||' ('||o.object_type||')' END
          FROM dba_objects o WHERE o.object_id(+) = e.current_obj# AND ROWNUM = 1)
       ), 1, 60) current_object_ff,
       e.timed_event timed_event_ff
  FROM events e,
       total t
 WHERE ROWNUM <= 20
   AND ROUND(100 * e.samples / t.samples, 1) > 0.1
 UNION ALL
SELECT others samples_ff,
       ROUND(100 * others / samples, 1) percent_ff,
       TO_NUMBER(NULL) plan_hash_value,
       TO_NUMBER(NULL) id,
       NULL operation_ff,
       NULL current_object_ff,
       'Others' timed_event_ff
  FROM total
 WHERE others > 0
   AND ROUND(100 * others / samples, 1) > 0.1

SELECT i.index_owner||'.'||i.index_name||' '||c.column_name index_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_ind_columns i,
       dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','A_LNGSLIST'),('THH_C4C','A_MEMBPCP'),('THH_C4C','A_USR'),('THH_C4C','A_USR_ADD'),('THH_C4C','A_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_A_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_USR'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','T_APBL'),('THH_C4C','T_APL'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_BLR_PLT'),('THH_C4C','T_CFRDREVW'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCT'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDS'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL_ITEMPVDRSSPS'),('THH_C4C','T_FAX_CSFNCASEPVDR'),('THH_C4C','T_FAX_CSFNRQNGPVDR'),('THH_C4C','T_FRDSAND_FMLYLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_FRTSFDRS'),('THH_C4C','T_GRP_MEMS'),('THH_C4C','T_LCNSLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_LWSTCOSTPVDR'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_ORG_CHRTITEM'),('THH_C4C','T_OTHER_INSURANCE'),('THH_C4C','T_PHI'),('THH_C4C','T_PROVIDER_CHOICE'),('THH_C4C','T_PRSC'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRADVEGRP_PVRS'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRASTN'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRPAYRDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRPLNSAFFS'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDR_DIR_DETAILS'),('THH_C4C','T_SVGSCAT_DTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_SYTMSTNGDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_TAKNASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_TNFRREC'),('THH_C4C','T_UM_CSFNRQNGPVRS'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_ADD'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_GRANT_DGIS_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_GRANT_RESTRICTED_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_WKFWTSK'),('THH_C4C','T_XMPTPVRS'))
   AND c.owner = i.table_owner
   AND c.table_name = i.table_name
   AND c.column_name = i.column_name
 ORDER BY
       i.index_owner,
       i.index_name,
       i.column_position

SELECT i.index_owner||'.'||i.index_name||' '||c.column_name index_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_ind_columns i,
       dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','A_LNGSLIST'),('THH_C4C','A_MEMBPCP'),('THH_C4C','A_USR'),('THH_C4C','A_USR_ADD'),('THH_C4C','A_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_A_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_USR'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','T_APBL'),('THH_C4C','T_APL'),('THH_C4C','T_APVLTRKGDEND'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_BLR_PLT'),('THH_C4C','T_CFRDREVW'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCT'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDS'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL_ITEMPVDRSSPS'),('THH_C4C','T_FAX_CSFNCASEPVDR'),('THH_C4C','T_FAX_CSFNRQNGPVDR'),('THH_C4C','T_FRDSAND_FMLYLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_FRTSFDRS'),('THH_C4C','T_GRP_MEMS'),('THH_C4C','T_LCNSLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_LWSTCOSTPVDR'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_ORG_CHRTITEM'),('THH_C4C','T_OTHER_INSURANCE'),('THH_C4C','T_PHI'),('THH_C4C','T_PROVIDER_CHOICE'),('THH_C4C','T_PRSC'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRADVEGRP_PVRS'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRASTN'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRPAYRDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRPLNSAFFS'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDR_DIR_DETAILS'),('THH_C4C','T_SVGSCAT_DTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_SYTMSTNGDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_TAKNASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_TNFRREC'),('THH_C4C','T_UM_CSFNRQNGPVRS'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_ADD'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_GRANT_DGIS_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_GRANT_RESTRICTED_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_WKFWTSK'),('THH_C4C','T_XMPTPVRS'))
   AND c.owner = i.table_owner
   AND c.table_name = i.table_name
   AND c.column_name = i.column_name
 ORDER BY
       i.index_owner,
       i.index_name,
       i.column_position

WITH
events AS (
SELECT /*+
       FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn)
       FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash)
       FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)
       USE_HASH(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)
       FULL(h.sn)
       FULL(h.ash)
       FULL(h.evt)
       USE_HASH(h.sn h.ash h.evt)
       */
       h.sql_plan_hash_value plan_hash_value,
       NVL(h.sql_plan_line_id, 0) line_id_ff,
       SUBSTR(h.sql_plan_operation||' '||h.sql_plan_options, 1, 50) operation_ff,
       CASE h.session_state WHEN 'ON CPU' THEN h.session_state ELSE h.wait_class||' "'||h.event||'"' END timed_event,
       COUNT(*) samples
  FROM dba_hist_active_sess_history h
 WHERE :license = 'Y'
   AND h.dbid = :dbid
   AND h.sql_id = :sql_id
   AND h.snap_id BETWEEN 3483 AND 4973
 GROUP BY
       h.sql_plan_hash_value,
       h.sql_plan_line_id,
       h.sql_plan_operation,
       h.sql_plan_options,
       CASE h.session_state WHEN 'ON CPU' THEN h.session_state ELSE h.wait_class||' "'||h.event||'"' END
 ORDER BY
       5 DESC
),
total AS (
SELECT SUM(samples) samples,
       SUM(CASE WHEN ROWNUM > 15 THEN samples ELSE 0 END) others
  FROM events
)
SELECT e.samples samples_ff,
       ROUND(100 * e.samples / t.samples, 1) percent_ff,
       e.plan_hash_value,
       e.line_id_ff,
       e.operation_ff,
       e.timed_event timed_event_ff
  FROM events e,
       total t
 WHERE ROWNUM <= 15
   AND ROUND(100 * e.samples / t.samples, 1) > 0.1
 UNION ALL
SELECT others samples_ff,
       ROUND(100 * others / samples, 1) percent_ff,
       TO_NUMBER(NULL) plan_hash_value,
       TO_NUMBER(NULL) id,
       NULL operation_ff,
       'Others' timed_event_ff
  FROM total
 WHERE others > 0
   AND ROUND(100 * others / samples, 1) > 0.1

SELECT i.index_owner||'.'||i.index_name||' '||c.column_name index_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_ind_columns i,
       dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','A_APBL'),('THH_C4C','A_CM_BASEBASE'),('THH_C4C','A_MEMBDGISBASE'),('THH_C4C','A_PVDRASTN'),('THH_C4C','A_UM_BASE'),('THH_C4C','A_USR'),('THH_C4C','MV_PATID_CM_COND_PROVIDER'))
   AND c.owner = i.table_owner
   AND c.table_name = i.table_name
   AND c.column_name = i.column_name
 ORDER BY
       i.index_owner,
       i.index_name,
       i.column_position

SELECT i.index_owner||'.'||i.index_name||' '||c.column_name index_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_ind_columns i,
       dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','A_APBL'),('THH_C4C','A_APBLSRVC'),('THH_C4C','A_MEMBDGISBASE'),('THH_C4C','A_USR'),('THH_C4C','MV_PATID_CLINIC_COND_SRVCD'),('THH_C4C','T_DRUGCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCLCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','T_SRVC'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'))
   AND c.owner = i.table_owner
   AND c.table_name = i.table_name
   AND c.column_name = i.column_name
 ORDER BY
       i.index_owner,
       i.index_name,
       i.column_position

WITH
events AS (
SELECT /*+
       FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn)
       FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash)
       FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)
       USE_HASH(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)
       FULL(h.sn)
       FULL(h.ash)
       FULL(h.evt)
       USE_HASH(h.sn h.ash h.evt)
       */
       CASE h.session_state WHEN 'ON CPU' THEN h.session_state ELSE h.wait_class||' "'||h.event||'"' END timed_event,
       COUNT(*) samples
  FROM dba_hist_active_sess_history h
 WHERE :license = 'Y'
   AND h.dbid = :dbid
   AND h.sql_id = :sql_id
   AND h.snap_id BETWEEN 3483 AND 4973
 GROUP BY
       CASE h.session_state WHEN 'ON CPU' THEN h.session_state ELSE h.wait_class||' "'||h.event||'"' END
 ORDER BY
       2 DESC
),
total AS (
SELECT SUM(samples) samples,
       SUM(CASE WHEN ROWNUM > 10 THEN samples ELSE 0 END) others
  FROM events
)
SELECT e.samples samples_ff,
       ROUND(100 * e.samples / t.samples, 1) percent_ff,
       e.timed_event timed_event_ff
  FROM events e,
       total t
 WHERE ROWNUM <= 10
   AND ROUND(100 * e.samples / t.samples, 1) > 0.1
 UNION ALL
SELECT others samples_ff,
       ROUND(100 * others / samples, 1) percent_ff,
       'Others' timed_event_ff
  FROM total
 WHERE others > 0
   AND ROUND(100 * others / samples, 1) > 0.1

WITH OBJECT AS ( SELECT /*+ MATERIALIZE */ OBJECT_OWNER OWNER, OBJECT_NAME 
  NAME FROM GV$SQL_PLAN WHERE INST_ID IN (SELECT INST_ID FROM GV$INSTANCE) 
  AND SQL_ID = :B1 AND OBJECT_OWNER IS NOT NULL AND OBJECT_NAME IS NOT NULL 
  UNION SELECT OBJECT_OWNER OWNER, OBJECT_NAME NAME FROM DBA_HIST_SQL_PLAN 
  WHERE :B3 = 'Y' AND DBID = :B2 AND SQL_ID = :B1 AND OBJECT_OWNER IS NOT 
  NULL AND OBJECT_NAME IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT CASE H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 
  THEN 'SYS' ELSE O.OWNER END OWNER, CASE H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 THEN 'UNDO' 
  ELSE O.OBJECT_NAME END NAME FROM GV$ACTIVE_SESSION_HISTORY H, DBA_OBJECTS O 
  WHERE :B3 = 'Y' AND H.SQL_ID = :B1 AND H.CURRENT_OBJ# >= 0 AND 
  O.OBJECT_ID(+) = H.CURRENT_OBJ# UNION SELECT /*+
               
  FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn)
               
  FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash)
               
  FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)
               
  USE_HASH(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn 
  h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)
   
              FULL(h.sn)
               FULL(h.ash)
               FULL(h.evt)
  
               USE_HASH(h.sn h.ash h.evt)
               */ CASE 
  H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 THEN 'SYS' ELSE O.OWNER END OWNER, CASE 
  H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 THEN 'UNDO' ELSE O.OBJECT_NAME END NAME FROM 
  DBA_HIST_ACTIVE_SESS_HISTORY H, DBA_OBJECTS O WHERE :B3 = 'Y' AND H.DBID = 
  :B2 AND H.SQL_ID = :B1 AND H.CURRENT_OBJ# >= 0 AND O.OBJECT_ID(+) = 
  H.CURRENT_OBJ# ) SELECT 'TABLE', T.OWNER, T.TABLE_NAME FROM 
  DBA_TAB_STATISTICS T, OBJECT O WHERE T.OWNER = O.OWNER AND T.TABLE_NAME = 
  O.NAME UNION SELECT 'TABLE', I.TABLE_OWNER, I.TABLE_NAME FROM DBA_INDEXES I,
   OBJECT O WHERE I.OWNER = O.OWNER AND I.INDEX_NAME = O.NAME

SELECT i.index_owner||'.'||i.index_name||' '||c.column_name index_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_ind_columns i,
       dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('SYS','KOTAD$'),('SYS','KOTTB$'),('SYS','USER$'),('SYS','WRM$_SNAPSHOT_DETAILS'),('THH_C4C','T_BCK_RLES'),('THH_C4C','T_ESCNRLES'),('THH_C4C','T_PRMR'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'),('THH_C4C','T_WKFWTSK'),('THH_C4C','T_WKFWTSK_STT_CNGE'))
   AND c.owner = i.table_owner
   AND c.table_name = i.table_name
   AND c.column_name = i.column_name
 ORDER BY
       i.index_owner,
       i.index_name,
       i.column_position

SELECT i.index_owner||'.'||i.index_name||' '||c.column_name index_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_ind_columns i,
       dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('SYS','ACLMVREFSTAT$'),('THH_C4C','FACT_ENROLLMENT'),('THH_C4C','T_BENSPKG'),('THH_C4C','T_ENNS'),('THH_C4C','T_INSCPRSRGRP'),('THH_C4C','T_PRODCAT'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'))
   AND c.owner = i.table_owner
   AND c.table_name = i.table_name
   AND c.column_name = i.column_name
 ORDER BY
       i.index_owner,
       i.index_name,
       i.column_position

SELECT i.index_owner||'.'||i.index_name||' '||c.column_name index_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_ind_columns i,
       dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','MV_PATID_THRESH_COND_CLAIM'),('THH_C4C','T_DRUGCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCLCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'))
   AND c.owner = i.table_owner
   AND c.table_name = i.table_name
   AND c.column_name = i.column_name
 ORDER BY
       i.index_owner,
       i.index_name,
       i.column_position

SELECT i.index_owner||'.'||i.index_name||' '||c.column_name index_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_ind_columns i,
       dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','A_USR_ADD'),('THH_C4C','A_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','MV_DIM_MEMBER_ADDR_TMPRL'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'))
   AND c.owner = i.table_owner
   AND c.table_name = i.table_name
   AND c.column_name = i.column_name
 ORDER BY
       i.index_owner,
       i.index_name,
       i.column_position

WITH OBJECT AS ( SELECT /*+ MATERIALIZE */ OBJECT_OWNER OWNER, OBJECT_NAME 
  NAME FROM GV$SQL_PLAN WHERE INST_ID IN (SELECT INST_ID FROM GV$INSTANCE) 
  AND SQL_ID = :B1 AND OBJECT_OWNER IS NOT NULL AND OBJECT_NAME IS NOT NULL 
  UNION SELECT OBJECT_OWNER OWNER, OBJECT_NAME NAME FROM DBA_HIST_SQL_PLAN 
  WHERE :B3 = 'Y' AND DBID = :B2 AND SQL_ID = :B1 AND OBJECT_OWNER IS NOT 
  NULL AND OBJECT_NAME IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT CASE H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 
  THEN 'SYS' ELSE O.OWNER END OWNER, CASE H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 THEN 'UNDO' 
  ELSE O.OBJECT_NAME END NAME FROM GV$ACTIVE_SESSION_HISTORY H, DBA_OBJECTS O 
  WHERE :B3 = 'Y' AND H.SQL_ID = :B1 AND H.CURRENT_OBJ# >= 0 AND 
  O.OBJECT_ID(+) = H.CURRENT_OBJ# UNION SELECT /*+
               
  FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn)
               
  FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash)
               
  FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)
               
  USE_HASH(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn 
  h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)
   
              FULL(h.sn)
               FULL(h.ash)
               FULL(h.evt)
  
               USE_HASH(h.sn h.ash h.evt)
               */ CASE 
  H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 THEN 'SYS' ELSE O.OWNER END OWNER, CASE 
  H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 THEN 'UNDO' ELSE O.OBJECT_NAME END NAME FROM 
  DBA_HIST_ACTIVE_SESS_HISTORY H, DBA_OBJECTS O WHERE :B3 = 'Y' AND H.DBID = 
  :B2 AND H.SQL_ID = :B1 AND H.CURRENT_OBJ# >= 0 AND O.OBJECT_ID(+) = 
  H.CURRENT_OBJ# ) SELECT 'TABLE', T.OWNER, T.TABLE_NAME FROM 
  DBA_TAB_STATISTICS T, OBJECT O WHERE T.OWNER = O.OWNER AND T.TABLE_NAME = 
  O.NAME UNION SELECT 'TABLE', I.TABLE_OWNER, I.TABLE_NAME FROM DBA_INDEXES I,
   OBJECT O WHERE I.OWNER = O.OWNER AND I.INDEX_NAME = O.NAME
