SELECT i.index_owner||'.'||i.index_name||' '||c.column_name index_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_ind_columns i,
       dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','CAREADMIN_LOG'),('THH_C4C','T_OTHER_INSURANCE'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'))
   AND c.owner = i.table_owner
   AND c.table_name = i.table_name
   AND c.column_name = i.column_name
 ORDER BY
       i.index_owner,
       i.index_name,
       i.column_position

SQL ID: 3pb4044qpq1jp Plan Hash: 1870352153

WITH OBJECT AS ( SELECT /*+ MATERIALIZE */ OBJECT_OWNER OWNER, OBJECT_NAME 
  NAME FROM GV$SQL_PLAN WHERE INST_ID IN (SELECT INST_ID FROM GV$INSTANCE) 
  AND SQL_ID = :B1 AND OBJECT_OWNER IS NOT NULL AND OBJECT_NAME IS NOT NULL 
  UNION SELECT OBJECT_OWNER OWNER, OBJECT_NAME NAME FROM DBA_HIST_SQL_PLAN 
  WHERE :B3 = 'Y' AND DBID = :B2 AND SQL_ID = :B1 AND OBJECT_OWNER IS NOT 
  NULL AND OBJECT_NAME IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT CASE H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 
  THEN 'SYS' ELSE O.OWNER END OWNER, CASE H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 THEN 'UNDO' 
  ELSE O.OBJECT_NAME END NAME FROM GV$ACTIVE_SESSION_HISTORY H, DBA_OBJECTS O 
  WHERE :B3 = 'Y' AND H.SQL_ID = :B1 AND H.CURRENT_OBJ# >= 0 AND 
  O.OBJECT_ID(+) = H.CURRENT_OBJ# UNION SELECT /*+
               
  FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn)
               
  FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash)
               
  FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)
               
  USE_HASH(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn 
  h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)
   
              FULL(h.sn)
               FULL(h.ash)
               FULL(h.evt)
  
               USE_HASH(h.sn h.ash h.evt)
               */ CASE 
  H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 THEN 'SYS' ELSE O.OWNER END OWNER, CASE 
  H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 THEN 'UNDO' ELSE O.OBJECT_NAME END NAME FROM 
  DBA_HIST_ACTIVE_SESS_HISTORY H, DBA_OBJECTS O WHERE :B3 = 'Y' AND H.DBID = 
  :B2 AND H.SQL_ID = :B1 AND H.CURRENT_OBJ# >= 0 AND O.OBJECT_ID(+) = 
  H.CURRENT_OBJ# ) SELECT 'TABLE', T.OWNER, T.TABLE_NAME FROM 
  DBA_TAB_STATISTICS T, OBJECT O WHERE T.OWNER = O.OWNER AND T.TABLE_NAME = 
  O.NAME UNION SELECT 'TABLE', I.TABLE_OWNER, I.TABLE_NAME FROM DBA_INDEXES I,
   OBJECT O WHERE I.OWNER = O.OWNER AND I.INDEX_NAME = O.NAME

SQL ID: 3pb4044qpq1jp Plan Hash: 3111128736

WITH OBJECT AS ( SELECT /*+ MATERIALIZE */ OBJECT_OWNER OWNER, OBJECT_NAME 
  NAME FROM GV$SQL_PLAN WHERE INST_ID IN (SELECT INST_ID FROM GV$INSTANCE) 
  AND SQL_ID = :B1 AND OBJECT_OWNER IS NOT NULL AND OBJECT_NAME IS NOT NULL 
  UNION SELECT OBJECT_OWNER OWNER, OBJECT_NAME NAME FROM DBA_HIST_SQL_PLAN 
  WHERE :B3 = 'Y' AND DBID = :B2 AND SQL_ID = :B1 AND OBJECT_OWNER IS NOT 
  NULL AND OBJECT_NAME IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT CASE H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 
  THEN 'SYS' ELSE O.OWNER END OWNER, CASE H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 THEN 'UNDO' 
  ELSE O.OBJECT_NAME END NAME FROM GV$ACTIVE_SESSION_HISTORY H, DBA_OBJECTS O 
  WHERE :B3 = 'Y' AND H.SQL_ID = :B1 AND H.CURRENT_OBJ# >= 0 AND 
  O.OBJECT_ID(+) = H.CURRENT_OBJ# UNION SELECT /*+
               
  FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn)
               
  FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash)
               
  FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)
               
  USE_HASH(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn 
  h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)
   
              FULL(h.sn)
               FULL(h.ash)
               FULL(h.evt)
  
               USE_HASH(h.sn h.ash h.evt)
               */ CASE 
  H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 THEN 'SYS' ELSE O.OWNER END OWNER, CASE 
  H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 THEN 'UNDO' ELSE O.OBJECT_NAME END NAME FROM 
  DBA_HIST_ACTIVE_SESS_HISTORY H, DBA_OBJECTS O WHERE :B3 = 'Y' AND H.DBID = 
  :B2 AND H.SQL_ID = :B1 AND H.CURRENT_OBJ# >= 0 AND O.OBJECT_ID(+) = 
  H.CURRENT_OBJ# ) SELECT 'TABLE', T.OWNER, T.TABLE_NAME FROM 
  DBA_TAB_STATISTICS T, OBJECT O WHERE T.OWNER = O.OWNER AND T.TABLE_NAME = 
  O.NAME UNION SELECT 'TABLE', I.TABLE_OWNER, I.TABLE_NAME FROM DBA_INDEXES I,
   OBJECT O WHERE I.OWNER = O.OWNER AND I.INDEX_NAME = O.NAME

WITH OBJECT AS ( SELECT /*+ MATERIALIZE */ OBJECT_OWNER OWNER, OBJECT_NAME

  UNION SELECT OBJECT_OWNER OWNER, OBJECT_NAME NAME FROM DBA_HIST_SQL_PLAN 
  WHERE :B3 = 'Y' AND DBID = :B2 AND SQL_ID = :B1 AND OBJECT_OWNER IS NOT 
  NULL AND OBJECT_NAME IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT CASE H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 
  THEN 'SYS' ELSE O.OWNER END OWNER, CASE H.CURRENT_OBJ# WHEN 0 THEN 'UNDO' 
  ELSE O.OBJECT_NAME END NAME FROM GV$ACTIVE_SESSION_HISTORY H, DBA_OBJECTS O 
  WHERE :B3 = 'Y' AND H.SQL_ID = :B1 AND H.CURRENT_OBJ# >= 0 AND

  H.CURRENT_OBJ# ) SELECT 'TABLE', T.OWNER, T.TABLE_NAME FROM

SELECT c.owner||'.'||c.table_name||' '||c.column_name table_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (c.owner, c.table_name) IN (('SYS','USER$'),('THH_ADDRESS','T_CITYOR_TOWN'),('THH_ADDRESS','T_CNTY'),('THH_C4C','A_RSPE'),('THH_C4C','A_RSPECHCS'),('THH_C4C','A_TAKNASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','CERME_CONFIG'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATADEF'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAENTRY'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUE'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUEDEF'),('THH_C4C','INSTRUCTION_CARD_ASSOC'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_CAREPLAN'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_CAREPLAN_MEMBDGISB'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','OPS_ACTIVITY_INCIDENT'),('THH_C4C','OPS_RELATED_DATA'),('THH_C4C','T_ALRT'),('THH_C4C','T_APBL'),('THH_C4C','T_ASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TMPT_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_BENSPKG'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_GOALCP_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_MEMBDGISBASE_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_TODO_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CHCE'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_BASEBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_CTCS'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCT'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCTDTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_COORDINATION_OF_BENEFITS'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDS'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDSMETADAT'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL_ITEM'),('THH_C4C','T_DGIS'),('THH_C4C','T_DGIS_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_EDNLCNTTDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_ENNS'),('THH_C4C','T_FIL'),('THH_C4C','T_FRDSAND_FMLYLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_FRMA'),('THH_C4C','T_FRM_CELLTXT'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TODO_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_GPI_CODE'),('THH_C4C','T_ICMGFAX'),('THH_C4C','T_INSCPRSRGRP'),('THH_C4C','T_LNGSLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_LTR_TMPT'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCLCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE_GOALCP_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE_OUTCOME_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_NOTE'),('THH_C4C','T_NTCE'),('THH_C4C','T_ORG_CHRTITEMPRSS'),('THH_C4C','T_OTHER_INSURANCE'),('THH_C4C','T_OUTCOME'),('THH_C4C','T_PAYRDGISSCTY'),('THH_C4C','T_PAYRROLS'),('THH_C4C',          0          0          0    TABLE ACCESS STORAGE FULL FIRST ROWS USER_EDITIONING$ (cr=9 pr=3 pw=0 time=6992 us cost=2 size=6 card=1)

SELECT i.index_owner||'.'||i.index_name||' '||c.column_name index_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_ind_columns i,
       dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','T_DDL_ITEM'),('THH_C4C','T_NOTE'),('THH_C4C_DW','DW_DIM_NOTE'),('THH_C4C_DW','RPT_CONSTANTS'))
   AND c.owner = i.table_owner
   AND c.table_name = i.table_name
   AND c.column_name = i.column_name
 ORDER BY
       i.index_owner,
       i.index_name,
       i.column_position

SELECT c.owner||'.'||c.table_name||' '||c.column_name table_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (c.owner, c.table_name) IN (('SYS','TRG_LOGON'),('SYS','USER$'),('SYS','WRM$_SNAPSHOT_DETAILS'),('THH_ADDRESS','T_CITYOR_TOWN'),('THH_C4C','A_FIL'),('THH_C4C','A_RSPE'),('THH_C4C','A_RSPECHCS'),('THH_C4C','A_TAKNASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','A_USR'),('THH_C4C','CERME_CONFIG'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAENTRY'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUE'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUEDEF'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUE_AUDIT'),('THH_C4C','EDCONTENTKEYS'),('THH_C4C','FACT_TMPT_VTB'),('THH_C4C','INSTRUCTION_CARD'),('THH_C4C','INSTRUCTION_CARD_ASSOC'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_CAREPLAN'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_CAREPLAN_MEMBDGISB'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','OPS_ACTIVITY_INCIDENT'),('THH_C4C','OPS_RELATED_DATA'),('THH_C4C','T_ALRT'),('THH_C4C','T_APBL'),('THH_C4C','T_ASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_ASMTLTR_HEDS'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TMPT_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_BENSPKG'),('THH_C4C','T_BEN_FIL'),('THH_C4C','T_BLR_PLT'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_GOALCP_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_MEMBDGISBASE_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_TODO_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CHCE'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_BASEBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_CTCS'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_PRJ_PERS'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCT'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCTDTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_COORDINATION_OF_BENEFITS'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDS'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDSMETADAT'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL_ITEM'),('THH_C4C','T_DGIS'),('THH_C4C','T_DGIS_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_DRUGCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_EDNLCNTTDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_ENNS'),('THH_C4C','T_FIL'),('THH_C4C','T_FRDSAND_FMLYLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_FRMA'),('THH_C4C','T_FRM_CELLTXT'),('THH_C4C','T_FRM_TTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TMP_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TODO_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_ICMGFAX'),('THH_C4C','T_INSCPRSRGRP'),('THH_C4C','T_LNGSLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_LTR_TMPT'),('THH_C4C','T_LTR_TMPTEDNLCNNS'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCLCLM'),('THH_C  ORDER BY

SELECT c.owner||'.'||c.table_name||' '||c.column_name table_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,

  FROM dba_tab_cols c

       c.table_name,

SELECT i.index_owner||'.'||i.index_name||' '||c.column_name index_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_ind_columns i,
       dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('SYS','ACLMVREFSTAT$'),('THH_C4C','MV_DIM_CLAIM'),('THH_C4C','T_DGIS'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCLCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_PLCEOF_SRVC'))
   AND c.owner = i.table_owner
   AND c.table_name = i.table_name
   AND c.column_name = i.column_name
 ORDER BY
       i.index_owner,
       i.index_name,
       i.column_position

    select xmlelement("statsgroup",
           
    xmlagg(cells_xml order by category))
      from (
        select category,
  
               xmlelement("cellstats",
                 
  xmlattributes(disp_category as "type"),
                 all_xml, cell_xml) 
  cells_xml
          from (
            select category, max(disp_category) 
  disp_category,
                   case 
                   when 
  max(cat_rq_s) is not null
                     or max(cat_mb_s) is not null
␀                     then xmlelement("cell",
                          
  xmlattributes('All' as "name",
                            max(num_cells)   
    as "num_cells"),
                          -- build XML for user reads 
  total
                          case
                          when 
  category = '1-ureads'
                           and (max(cat_rq_s) is not 
  null
                            or  max(cat_mb_s) is not null)
            
                then xmlelement("stat",
                                 
  xmlattributes('fcior'     as "name",
                                   
  round(max(cat_rq_s),2)   as "rq",
                                   
  round(max(cat_rqps_s),2) as "rqps",
                                   
  round(max(cat_mb_s),2)   as "mb",
                                   
  round(max(cat_mbps_s),2) as "mbps"))
                           end,
       
                     xmlagg(all_xml order by rn),
                          
  -- add XML for partial writes
                          case when category =
   '2-uwrites'
                           and (max(fciorqwp_s) is not null
   
                           or  max(fciombwp_s) is not null)
                  
          then xmlelement("stat",
                                 
  xmlattributes('fciowp'     as "name",
                                   
  round(max(fciorqwp_s),2) as "rq",
                                   
  round(max(fciorqwp_ps_s),2)
                                                
              as "rqps",
                                   
  round(max(fciombwp_s),2) as "mb",
                                   
  round(max(fciombwp_ps_s),2)
                                                
              as "mbps",
                                -- calculate % of 
  total
                                round(
                               
    100*max(fciorqwp_s)/
                                    decode(
         
                               max(cat_rq_s),0,null,
                         
                 max(cat_rq_s)),2) as "rqpct",
                               
   -- calculate % of total
                                round(
            
                        100*max(fciombwp_s)/
                                 
     decode(
                                      max(cat_mb_s),0,null,
     
                                     max(cat_mb_s)),2) as "mbpct"))
          
                   end)
                    end all_xml,
                   
  xmlagg(cell_xml order by rn) cell_xml
              from (
                
  select cat.category, rn, max(cat.cat_disp) disp_category,
                  
       max(num_cells)     num_cells,
                       max(cat_rq_s)     
   cat_rq_s,
                       max(cat_mb_s)      cat_mb_s,
             
            max(cat_rqps_s)    cat_rqps_s,
                       
  max(cat_mbps_s)    cat_mbps_s,
                       max(fciorqwp_s)    
  fciorqwp_s,
                       max(fciorqwp_ps_s) fciorqwp_ps_s,
       
                  max(fciombwp_s)    fciombwp_s,
                       
  max(fciombwp_ps_s) fciombwp_ps_s,
                       -- build XML for 
  'All' node
                       xmlagg(
                         case 
   
                        when rn_stat = 1 
                          and (rq_s 
  is not null
                           or  mb_s is not null)
               
            then xmlelement("stat",
                                
  xmlattributes(
                                  decode(stat_name,
         
                                   'fcoior','fcioroltp',
                     
                       'fcsior','fciordw',
                                   
         'fcoiorqrm','fciorm',
                                           
  stat_name)    as "name",
                                  round(rq_s,2)   
  as "rq",
                                  round(rqps_s,2) as "rqps",
      
                              round(mb_s,2)   as "mb",
                       
             round(mbps_s,2) as "mbps",
                                  -- 
  additional efficiency stats
                                  
  decode(stat_name,'fcoior',
                                         
  round(eff_denom_s-rq_s,2))
                                                 
        as "misses",
                                  decode(stat_name,
  'fcsior',
                                         
  round(eff_denom_s/1048576,
                                               2)
  )     as "att",
                                  decode(stat_name,'fcsior',
  
                                         round(eff_denom_s/1048576/
       
                                         :duration,2))
                       
                                  as "attps",
                                
    decode(stat_name,'fccior',
                                         
  round(eff_denom_s/1048576,
                                               2)
  )     as "elig",
                                  decode(stat_name,
  'fccior',
                                         round(fcciobysave_s/
    
                                             1048576,2))
                     
                                    as "save",
                               
     case
                                  when stat_name in ('fcoior',
     
                                                  'fckpior',
                 
                                      'fcsior',
                              
                         'fccior')
                                  then 
  round(eff_s,2)
                                   end                as 
  "ratio",
                                  decode(stat_category,
           
                           '2-uwrites',round(rq_pct_s,2))
                    
                                     as "rqpct",
                             
       decode(stat_category,
                                    '2-uwrites',
  round(by_pct_s,2))
                                                       
  as "mbpct"))
                          end
                        order by 
  stat_name) all_xml,
                       case 
                       
  when cell_name is not null
                        and (max(cat_rq) is not 
  null 
                         or max(cat_mb) is not null)
                 
        then xmlelement("cell",
                              
  xmlattributes(cell_name as "name",
                                         
     rn        as "rn"),
                              -- add XML for user 
  reads total
                              case
                             
   when category = '1-ureads'
                               and (max(cat_rq) 
  is not null
                                or max(cat_mb) is not null)
    
                            then xmlelement("stat",
                          
             xmlattributes('fcior'    as "name",
                             
            round(max(cat_rq),2)   as "rq",
                                  
       round(max(cat_rqps),2) as "rqps",
                                     
    round(max(cat_mb),2)   as "mb",
                                       
  round(max(cat_mbps),2) as "mbps"))
                               end,
     
                           xmlagg(
                                case
      
                            when rq is not null or mb is not null
            
                      then xmlelement("stat",
                                
         xmlattributes(
                                         
  decode(stat_name,'fcoior','fcioroltp',
                                     
                       'fcsior','fciordw',
                                   
                         'fcoiorqrm','fciorm',
                               
                              stat_name)
                                     
                               as "name",
                                    
       round(rq,2)   as "rq",
                                         
  round(rqps,2) as "rqps",
                                         round(mb,
  2)   as "mb",
                                         round(mbps,2) as 
  "mbps",
                                         -- additional efficiency 
  stats
                                         decode(stat_name,'fcoior',
  
                                                round(eff_denom - rq,2))
     
                                                               as "misses",
  
                                         decode(stat_name,'fcsior',
          
                                        round(eff_denom/1048576,2))
          
                                                          as "att",
          
                                 decode(stat_name,'fcsior',
                  
                                round(eff_denom/1048576/
                     
                                  :duration,2))
                              
                                      as "attps",
                            
               decode(stat_name,'fccior',
                                    
              round(eff_denom/1048576,2))
                                    
                                as "elig",
                                   
        decode(stat_name,'fccior',
                                           
       round(fcciobysave/1048576,2))
                                         
                           as "save",
                                        
   case
                                         when stat_name in ('fcoior',
␀                                                              'fckpior',
     
                                                         'fcsior',
           
                                                   'fccior')
                 
                          then round(eff,2)
                                  
          end                     as "ratio",
                                
           decode(stat_category,
                                           
  '2-uwrites',round(rq_pct,2))
                                               
                     as "rqpct",
                                         
  decode(stat_category,
                                           
  '2-uwrites',round(by_pct,2))
                                               
                     as "mbpct"))
                                 end
       
                          order by stat_name),
                               
  -- add XML for partial writes
                               case
          
                       when category = '2-uwrites'
                           
       and (max(fciorqwp) is not null
                                 or 
  max(fciombwp) is not null)
                               then 
  xmlelement("stat",
                                      
  xmlattributes('fciowp'      as "name",
                                     
     round(max(fciorqwp),2)    as "rq",
                                      
    round(max(fciorqwp_ps),2) as "rqps",
                                     
     round(max(fciombwp),2)    as "mb",
                                      
    round(max(fciombwp_ps),2) as "mbps",
                                     
     -- calculate % of total
                                        round(
  
                                          100*max(fciorqwp)/
                 
                             decode(
                                         
       max(cat_rq),0,null,
                                                
  max(cat_rq)),2)   as "rqpct",
                                        -- 
  calculate % of total
                                        round(
        
                                    100*max(fciombwp)/
                       
                       decode(
                                              
  max(cat_mb),0,null,
                                                
  max(cat_mb)),2)   as "mbpct"))
                                 end)
       
                   end cell_xml
                   from cell_stats s,
        
              (select distinct category,
                            
  decode(category,'1-ureads','fc_ureads',
                                    
          '2-uwrites','fc_uwrites',
                                          
    '3-ireads','fc_ireads',
                                            
  '4-iwrites','fc_iwrites',
                                            
  '5-fcsrep','fcs_pop',
                                            
  substr(category,3)) cat_disp
                       from 
  xmltable('/stats/stat'
                              passing 
  xmltype(:fc_metadata) columns
                                category  
  varchar2(32) path '@cat')) cat
                  where s.stat_category (+) =
   cat.category
                    and nvl(s.rn,0)        <= :top_cells
     
               group by cat.category, rn, cell_name)
              group by 
  category))

SELECT i.table_owner||'.'||i.table_name||' '||i.owner||'.'||i.index_name table_and_index_name,
       i.partitioned,
       i.degree,
       i.index_type,
       i.uniqueness,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM dba_ind_columns ic WHERE ic.index_owner = i.owner AND ic.index_name = i.index_name) columns,
       i.status,
       i.visibility,
       i.blevel,
       i.leaf_blocks,
       i.distinct_keys,
       i.clustering_factor,
       i.num_rows,
       i.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(i.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       i.global_stats
  FROM dba_indexes i
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('SYS','USER$'),('THH_ADDRESS','T_CITYOR_TOWN'),('THH_ADDRESS','T_CNTY'),('THH_C4C','A_RSPE'),('THH_C4C','A_RSPECHCS'),('THH_C4C','A_TAKNASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','CERME_CONFIG'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATADEF'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAENTRY'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUE'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUEDEF'),('THH_C4C','INSTRUCTION_CARD_ASSOC'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_CAREPLAN'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_CAREPLAN_MEMBDGISB'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','OPS_ACTIVITY_INCIDENT'),('THH_C4C','OPS_RELATED_DATA'),('THH_C4C','T_ALRT'),('THH_C4C','T_APBL'),('THH_C4C','T_ASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TMPT_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_BENSPKG'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_GOALCP_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_MEMBDGISBASE_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_TODO_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CHCE'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_BASEBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_CTCS'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCT'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCTDTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_COORDINATION_OF_BENEFITS'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDS'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDSMETADAT'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL_ITEM'),('THH_C4C','T_DGIS'),('THH_C4C','T_DGIS_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_EDNLCNTTDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_ENNS'),('THH_C4C','T_FIL'),('THH_C4C','T_FRDSAND_FMLYLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_FRMA'),('THH_C4C','T_FRM_CELLTXT'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TODO_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_GPI_CODE'),('THH_C4C','T_ICMGFAX'),('THH_C4C','T_INSCPRSRGRP'),('THH_C4C','T_LNGSLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_LTR_TMPT'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCLCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE_GOALCP_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE_OUTCOME_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_NOTE'),('THH_C4C','T_NTCE'),('THH_C4C','T_ORG_CHRTITEMPRSS'),('THH_C4C','T_OTHER_INSURANCE'),('THH_C4C','T_OUTCOME'),('THH_C4C','T_PAYRDGISSCTY'),('THH_C4C','T_PAYRROLS'),('THH_C4C',        i.owner,
       i.index_name

SELECT i.table_owner||'.'||i.table_name||' '||i.owner||'.'||i.index_name table_and_index_name,
       i.partitioned,
       i.degree,
       i.index_type,
       i.uniqueness,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM dba_ind_columns ic WHERE ic.index_owner = i.owner AND ic.index_name = i.index_name) columns,
       i.status,
       i.visibility,
       i.blevel,
       i.leaf_blocks,
       i.distinct_keys,
       i.clustering_factor,
       i.num_rows,
       i.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(i.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       i.global_stats
  FROM dba_indexes i
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('SYS','TRG_LOGON'),('SYS','USER$'),('SYS','WRM$_SNAPSHOT_DETAILS'),('THH_ADDRESS','T_CITYOR_TOWN'),('THH_C4C','A_FIL'),('THH_C4C','A_RSPE'),('THH_C4C','A_RSPECHCS'),('THH_C4C','A_TAKNASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','A_USR'),('THH_C4C','CERME_CONFIG'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAENTRY'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUE'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUEDEF'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUE_AUDIT'),('THH_C4C','EDCONTENTKEYS'),('THH_C4C','FACT_TMPT_VTB'),('THH_C4C','INSTRUCTION_CARD'),('THH_C4C','INSTRUCTION_CARD_ASSOC'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_CAREPLAN'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_CAREPLAN_MEMBDGISB'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','OPS_ACTIVITY_INCIDENT'),('THH_C4C','OPS_RELATED_DATA'),('THH_C4C','T_ALRT'),('THH_C4C','T_APBL'),('THH_C4C','T_ASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_ASMTLTR_HEDS'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TMPT_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_BENSPKG'),('THH_C4C','T_BEN_FIL'),('THH_C4C','T_BLR_PLT'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_GOALCP_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_MEMBDGISBASE_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_TODO_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CHCE'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_BASEBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_CTCS'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_PRJ_PERS'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCT'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCTDTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_COORDINATION_OF_BENEFITS'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDS'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDSMETADAT'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL_ITEM'),('THH_C4C','T_DGIS'),('THH_C4C','T_DGIS_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_DRUGCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_EDNLCNTTDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_ENNS'),('THH_C4C','T_FIL'),('THH_C4C','T_FRDSAND_FMLYLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_FRMA'),('THH_C4C','T_FRM_CELLTXT'),('THH_C4C','T_FRM_TTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TMP_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TODO_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_ICMGFAX'),('THH_C4C','T_INSCPRSRGRP'),('THH_C4C','T_LNGSLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_LTR_TMPT'),('THH_C4C','T_LTR_TMPTEDNLCNNS'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCLCLM'),('THH_C  ORDER BY
       i.table_owner,
       i.table_name,
       i.owner,
       i.index_name

SELECT i.table_owner||'.'||i.table_name||' '||i.owner||'.'||i.index_name table_and_index_name,
       i.partitioned,
       i.degree,
       i.index_type,
       i.uniqueness,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM dba_ind_columns ic WHERE ic.index_owner = i.owner AND ic.index_name = i.index_name) columns,
       i.status,
       i.visibility,
       i.blevel,
       i.leaf_blocks,
       i.distinct_keys,
       i.clustering_factor,
       i.num_rows,
       i.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(i.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       i.global_stats
  FROM dba_indexes i
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('SYS','USER$'),('SYS','WRM$_SNAPSHOT_DETAILS'),('THH_ADDRESS','T_CITYOR_TOWN'),('THH_C4C','A_RSPECHCS'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAENTRY'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUE'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_CAREPLAN_MEMBDGISB'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','OPS_ACTIVITY_INCIDENT'),('THH_C4C','T_ALRT'),('THH_C4C','T_ASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TMPT_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_BENSPKG'),('THH_C4C','T_BEN_FIL'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_GOALCP_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_MEMBDGISBASE_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_TODO_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_BASEBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_CTCS'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_PRJ_PERS'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCT'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCTDTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_COORDINATION_OF_BENEFITS'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDS'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDSMETADAT'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL_ITEM'),('THH_C4C','T_DGIS'),('THH_C4C','T_DRUGCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_EDNLCNTTDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_ENNS'),('THH_C4C','T_FIL'),('THH_C4C','T_FRDSAND_FMLYLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_FRMA'),('THH_C4C','T_FRM_CELLTXT'),('THH_C4C','T_FRM_TTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TMP_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TODO_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_INSCPRSRGRP'),('THH_C4C','T_LNGSLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_LTR_TMPT'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCLCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE_GOALCP_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE_OUTCOME_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_NOTE'),('THH_C4C','T_NTCE'),('THH_C4C','T_OTHER_INSURANCE'),('THH_C4C','T_OUTCOME'),('THH_C4C','T_PAYRDGISSCTY'),('THH_C4C','T_PAYRROLS'),('THH_C4C','T_PHI'),('THH_C4C','T_PRMR'),('THH_C4C','T_PRODCAT'),('THH_C4C','T_PROVIDER_CHOICE'),('THH_C4C','T_PROVIDER_CHOICE_ROLE_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_PRSC'),('THH_C4C','T_QTN'),('THH_C4C','T_REVWHEAD'),('THH_C4C','T_REVWREC'),('THH_C4C','T_RSPE'),('THH_C4C','T_RSPECHCS'),('THH_C4C','T_SENTTSK'),('THH_C4C','T_TAKNASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_TNFRREC'),('THH_C4C','T_TODO'),('THH_C4C','T_TOD        i.table_owner,
       i.table_name,
       i.owner,
       i.index_name

SELECT i.index_owner||'.'||i.index_name||' '||c.column_name index_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_ind_columns i,
       dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('SYS','ACLMVREFSTAT$'),('THH_C4C','MV_DIM_ENROLLMENT'),('THH_C4C','T_BENSPKG'),('THH_C4C','T_ENNS'),('THH_C4C','T_INSCPRSRGRP'),('THH_C4C','T_PRODCAT'))
   AND c.owner = i.table_owner
   AND c.table_name = i.table_name
   AND c.column_name = i.column_name
 ORDER BY
       i.index_owner,
       i.index_name,
       i.column_position

SELECT owner||'.'||table_name table_name,
       partitioned,
       degree,
       temporary,
       blocks,
       num_rows,
       avg_row_len,
       sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       global_stats,
       compression
  FROM dba_tables
 WHERE (owner, table_name) IN (('SYS','TRG_LOGON'),('SYS','USER$'),('SYS','WRM$_SNAPSHOT_DETAILS'),('THH_ADDRESS','T_CITYOR_TOWN'),('THH_C4C','A_FIL'),('THH_C4C','A_RSPE'),('THH_C4C','A_RSPECHCS'),('THH_C4C','A_TAKNASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','A_USR'),('THH_C4C','CERME_CONFIG'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAENTRY'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUE'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUEDEF'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUE_AUDIT'),('THH_C4C','EDCONTENTKEYS'),('THH_C4C','FACT_TMPT_VTB'),('THH_C4C','INSTRUCTION_CARD'),('THH_C4C','INSTRUCTION_CARD_ASSOC'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_CAREPLAN'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_CAREPLAN_MEMBDGISB'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','OPS_ACTIVITY_INCIDENT'),('THH_C4C','OPS_RELATED_DATA'),('THH_C4C','T_ALRT'),('THH_C4C','T_APBL'),('THH_C4C','T_ASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_ASMTLTR_HEDS'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TMPT_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_BENSPKG'),('THH_C4C','T_BEN_FIL'),('THH_C4C','T_BLR_PLT'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_GOALCP_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_MEMBDGISBASE_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_TODO_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CHCE'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_BASEBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_CTCS'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_PRJ_PERS'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCT'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCTDTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_COORDINATION_OF_BENEFITS'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDS'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDSMETADAT'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL_ITEM'),('THH_C4C','T_DGIS'),('THH_C4C','T_DGIS_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_DRUGCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_EDNLCNTTDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_ENNS'),('THH_C4C','T_FIL'),('THH_C4C','T_FRDSAND_FMLYLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_FRMA'),('THH_C4C','T_FRM_CELLTXT'),('THH_C4C','T_FRM_TTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TMP_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TODO_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_ICMGFAX'),('THH_C4C','T_INSCPRSRGRP'),('THH_C4C','T_LNGSLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_LTR_TMPT'),('THH_C4C','T_LTR_TMPTEDNLCNNS'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCLCLM'),('THH_C        partitioned,

SELECT c.owner||'.'||c.table_name||' '||c.column_name table_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (c.owner, c.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','A_LNGSLIST'),('THH_C4C','A_MEMBPCP'),('THH_C4C','A_USR'),('THH_C4C','A_USR_ADD'),('THH_C4C','A_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_A_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_USR'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','T_APBL'),('THH_C4C','T_APL'),('THH_C4C','T_APVLTRKGDEND'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_BLR_PLT'),('THH_C4C','T_CFRDREVW'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCT'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDS'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL_ITEMPVDRSSPS'),('THH_C4C','T_FAX_CSFNCASEPVDR'),('THH_C4C','T_FAX_CSFNRQNGPVDR'),('THH_C4C','T_FRDSAND_FMLYLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_FRTSFDRS'),('THH_C4C','T_GRP_MEMS'),('THH_C4C','T_LCNSLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_LWSTCOSTPVDR'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_ORG_CHRTITEM'),('THH_C4C','T_OTHER_INSURANCE'),('THH_C4C','T_PHI'),('THH_C4C','T_PROVIDER_CHOICE'),('THH_C4C','T_PRSC'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRADVEGRP_PVRS'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRASTN'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRPAYRDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRPLNSAFFS'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDR_DIR_DETAILS'),('THH_C4C','T_SVGSCAT_DTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_SYTMSTNGDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_TAKNASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_TNFRREC'),('THH_C4C','T_UM_CSFNRQNGPVRS'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_ADD'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_GRANT_DGIS_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_GRANT_RESTRICTED_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_WKFWTSK'),('THH_C4C','T_XMPTPVRS'))
 ORDER BY
       c.owner,
       c.table_name,
       c.column_name

SELECT owner||'.'||table_name table_name,
       partitioned,
       degree,
       temporary,
       blocks,
       num_rows,
       avg_row_len,
       sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       global_stats,
       compression
  FROM dba_tables
 WHERE (owner, table_name) IN (('SYS','USER$'),('SYS','WRM$_SNAPSHOT_DETAILS'),('THH_ADDRESS','T_CITYOR_TOWN'),('THH_C4C','A_RSPECHCS'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAENTRY'),('THH_C4C','CLINICALDATAVALUE'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_CAREPLAN_MEMBDGISB'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','OPS_ACTIVITY_INCIDENT'),('THH_C4C','T_ALRT'),('THH_C4C','T_ASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TMPT_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_BENSPKG'),('THH_C4C','T_BEN_FIL'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_GOALCP_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_MEMBDGISBASE_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CAREPLAN_TODO_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_BASEBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_CTCS'),('THH_C4C','T_CM_PRJ_PERS'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCT'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCTDTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_COORDINATION_OF_BENEFITS'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDS'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDSMETADAT'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL_ITEM'),('THH_C4C','T_DGIS'),('THH_C4C','T_DRUGCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_EDNLCNTTDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_ENNS'),('THH_C4C','T_FIL'),('THH_C4C','T_FRDSAND_FMLYLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_FRMA'),('THH_C4C','T_FRM_CELLTXT'),('THH_C4C','T_FRM_TTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TMP_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_GOALCP_TODO_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_INSCPRSRGRP'),('THH_C4C','T_LNGSLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_LTR_TMPT'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCLCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE_GOALCP_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE_OUTCOME_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_NOTE'),('THH_C4C','T_NTCE'),('THH_C4C','T_OTHER_INSURANCE'),('THH_C4C','T_OUTCOME'),('THH_C4C','T_PAYRDGISSCTY'),('THH_C4C','T_PAYRROLS'),('THH_C4C','T_PHI'),('THH_C4C','T_PRMR'),('THH_C4C','T_PRODCAT'),('THH_C4C','T_PROVIDER_CHOICE'),('THH_C4C','T_PROVIDER_CHOICE_ROLE_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_PRSC'),('THH_C4C','T_QTN'),('THH_C4C','T_REVWHEAD'),('THH_C4C','T_REVWREC'),('THH_C4C','T_RSPE'),('THH_C4C','T_RSPECHCS'),('THH_C4C','T_SENTTSK'),('THH_C4C','T_TAKNASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_TNFRREC'),('THH_C4C','T_TODO'),('THH_C4C','T_TODO_DDL_ITEM_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_TODO_NOTE_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_TODO_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_TSK_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_TSK_TMPTAMTS'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_ADD'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_PREFERENCES'),('THH_C4C','T_WKFWTSK'))
 ORDER BY
       owner,
       table_name

SELECT c.owner||'.'||c.table_name||' '||c.column_name table_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_tab_cols c

WITH v AS (
SELECT /*+ MATERIALIZE */
       DISTINCT sql_id, plan_hash_value, dbid, timestamp
  FROM dba_hist_sql_plan
 WHERE :license = 'Y'
   AND dbid = :dbid
   AND sql_id = :sql_id
 ORDER BY 1, 2, 3 )
SELECT /*+ ORDERED USE_NL(t) */
       TO_CHAR(v.timestamp, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') plan_timestamp_ff,
       t.plan_table_output
  FROM v, TABLE(DBMS_XPLAN.DISPLAY_AWR(v.sql_id, v.plan_hash_value, v.dbid, 'ADVANCED')) t
