SELECT c.owner||'.'||c.table_name||' '||c.column_name table_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (c.owner, c.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','A_USR_ADD'),('THH_C4C','A_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','MV_DIM_MEMBER_ADDR_TMPRL'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'))
 ORDER BY
       c.owner,
       c.table_name,
       c.column_name

SELECT c.owner||'.'||c.table_name||' '||c.column_name table_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (c.owner, c.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','MV_PATID_THRESH_COND_CLAIM'),('THH_C4C','T_DRUGCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCLCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'))
 ORDER BY
       c.owner,
       c.table_name,
       c.column_name

SELECT c.owner||'.'||c.table_name||' '||c.column_name table_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (c.owner, c.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','CAREADMIN_LOG'),('THH_C4C','T_OTHER_INSURANCE'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'))
 ORDER BY
       c.owner,
       c.table_name,
       c.column_name

SELECT i.table_owner||'.'||i.table_name||' '||i.owner||'.'||i.index_name table_and_index_name,
       i.partitioned,
       i.degree,
       i.index_type,
       i.uniqueness,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM dba_ind_columns ic WHERE ic.index_owner = i.owner AND ic.index_name = i.index_name) columns,
       i.status,
       i.visibility,
       i.blevel,
       i.leaf_blocks,
       i.distinct_keys,
       i.clustering_factor,
       i.num_rows,
       i.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(i.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       i.global_stats
  FROM dba_indexes i
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('SYS','KOTAD$'),('SYS','KOTTB$'),('SYS','USER$'),('SYS','WRM$_SNAPSHOT_DETAILS'),('THH_C4C','T_BCK_RLES'),('THH_C4C','T_ESCNRLES'),('THH_C4C','T_PRMR'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'),('THH_C4C','T_WKFWTSK'),('THH_C4C','T_WKFWTSK_STT_CNGE'))
 ORDER BY
       i.table_owner,
       i.table_name,
       i.owner,
       i.index_name

SELECT i.table_owner||'.'||i.table_name||' '||i.owner||'.'||i.index_name table_and_index_name,
       i.partitioned,
       i.degree,
       i.index_type,
       i.uniqueness,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM dba_ind_columns ic WHERE ic.index_owner = i.owner AND ic.index_name = i.index_name) columns,
       i.status,
       i.visibility,
       i.blevel,
       i.leaf_blocks,
       i.distinct_keys,
       i.clustering_factor,
       i.num_rows,
       i.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(i.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       i.global_stats
  FROM dba_indexes i
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','A_APBL'),('THH_C4C','A_APBLSRVC'),('THH_C4C','A_MEMBDGISBASE'),('THH_C4C','A_USR'),('THH_C4C','MV_PATID_CLINIC_COND_SRVCD'),('THH_C4C','T_DRUGCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCLCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','T_SRVC'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'))
 ORDER BY
       i.table_owner,
       i.table_name,
       i.owner,
       i.index_name

SELECT owner||'.'||table_name table_name,
       partitioned,
       degree,
       temporary,
       blocks,
       num_rows,
       avg_row_len,
       sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       global_stats,
       compression
  FROM dba_tables
 WHERE (owner, table_name) IN (('SYS','KOTAD$'),('SYS','KOTTB$'),('SYS','USER$'),('SYS','WRM$_SNAPSHOT_DETAILS'),('THH_C4C','T_BCK_RLES'),('THH_C4C','T_ESCNRLES'),('THH_C4C','T_PRMR'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'),('THH_C4C','T_WKFWTSK'),('THH_C4C','T_WKFWTSK_STT_CNGE'))
 ORDER BY
       owner,
       table_name

SELECT i.table_owner||'.'||i.table_name||' '||i.owner||'.'||i.index_name table_and_index_name,
       i.partitioned,
       i.degree,
       i.index_type,
       i.uniqueness,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM dba_ind_columns ic WHERE ic.index_owner = i.owner AND ic.index_name = i.index_name) columns,
       i.status,
       i.visibility,
       i.blevel,
       i.leaf_blocks,
       i.distinct_keys,
       i.clustering_factor,
       i.num_rows,
       i.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(i.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       i.global_stats
  FROM dba_indexes i
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','A_APBL'),('THH_C4C','A_CM_BASEBASE'),('THH_C4C','A_MEMBDGISBASE'),('THH_C4C','A_PVDRASTN'),('THH_C4C','A_UM_BASE'),('THH_C4C','A_USR'),('THH_C4C','MV_PATID_CM_COND_PROVIDER'))
 ORDER BY
       i.table_owner,
       i.table_name,
       i.owner,
       i.index_name

SELECT i.table_owner||'.'||i.table_name||' '||i.owner||'.'||i.index_name table_and_index_name,
       i.partitioned,
       i.degree,
       i.index_type,
       i.uniqueness,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM dba_ind_columns ic WHERE ic.index_owner = i.owner AND ic.index_name = i.index_name) columns,
       i.status,
       i.visibility,
       i.blevel,
       i.leaf_blocks,
       i.distinct_keys,
       i.clustering_factor,
       i.num_rows,
       i.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(i.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       i.global_stats
  FROM dba_indexes i
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('SYS','ACLMVREFSTAT$'),('THH_C4C','FACT_ENROLLMENT'),('THH_C4C','T_BENSPKG'),('THH_C4C','T_ENNS'),('THH_C4C','T_INSCPRSRGRP'),('THH_C4C','T_PRODCAT'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'))
 ORDER BY
       i.table_owner,
       i.table_name,
       i.owner,
       i.index_name

SELECT owner||'.'||table_name table_name,
       partitioned,
       degree,
       temporary,
       blocks,
       num_rows,
       avg_row_len,
       sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       global_stats,
       compression
  FROM dba_tables
 WHERE (owner, table_name) IN (('SYS','ACLMVREFSTAT$'),('THH_C4C','FACT_ENROLLMENT'),('THH_C4C','T_BENSPKG'),('THH_C4C','T_ENNS'),('THH_C4C','T_INSCPRSRGRP'),('THH_C4C','T_PRODCAT'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'))
 ORDER BY
       owner,
       table_name

SELECT EXTRACTVALUE(VALUE(D), '/row/@op'), EXTRACTVALUE(VALUE(D), '/row/@dis')

SELECT c.owner||'.'||c.table_name||' '||c.column_name table_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (c.owner, c.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_MEMBCTCS'),('THH_C4C','T_PROVIDER_CHOICE'),('THH_C4C','T_PROVIDER_CHOICE_ROLE_XREF'))
 ORDER BY
       c.owner,
       c.table_name,
       c.column_name

       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (c.owner, c.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','T_PROVIDER_CHOICE'))
 ORDER BY
       c.owner,
       c.table_name,
       c.column_name

       partitioned,
       degree,

       global_stats,
       compression
  FROM dba_tables

 ORDER BY
       owner,
       table_name

SELECT c.owner||'.'||c.table_name||' '||c.column_name table_and_column_name,
       c.data_type,
       c.nullable,
       c.data_default,
       c.num_distinct,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.low_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.low_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.low_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.low_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.low_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.low_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
       END low_value_translated,
       CASE WHEN c.data_type = 'NUMBER' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_number(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('VARCHAR2', 'CHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type IN ('NVARCHAR2','NCHAR') THEN SUBSTR(to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_nvarchar2(c.high_value)),1,32)
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_DOUBLE' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_double(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'BINARY_FLOAT' THEN to_char(utl_raw.cast_to_binary_float(c.high_value))
        WHEN c.data_type = 'DATE' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00')))
        WHEN c.data_type LIKE 'TIMESTAMP%' THEN rtrim(
                    ltrim(to_char(100*(to_number(substr(c.high_value,1,2) ,'XX')-100) + (to_number(substr(c.high_value,3,2) ,'XX')-100),'0000'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,5,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'-'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,7,2) ,'XX')  ,'00'))||'/'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,9,2) ,'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,11,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||':'||
                    ltrim(to_char(     to_number(substr(c.high_value,13,2),'XX')-1,'00'))||'.'||
                    to_number(substr(c.high_value,15,8),'XXXXXXXX'))
        END high_value_translated,
       c.density,
       c.num_nulls,
       c.num_buckets,
       c.histogram,
       c.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(c.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       c.global_stats,
       c.avg_col_len
  FROM dba_tab_cols c
 WHERE (c.owner, c.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','T_ENNS'))
 ORDER BY
       c.owner,
       c.table_name,
       c.column_name

SELECT owner||'.'||table_name table_name,
       partitioned,
       degree,
       temporary,
       blocks,
       num_rows,
       avg_row_len,
       sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       global_stats,
       compression
  FROM dba_tables
 WHERE (owner, table_name) IN (('SYS','ACLMVREFSTAT$'),('THH_C4C','MV_DIM_CLAIM'),('THH_C4C','T_DGIS'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCLCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_PLCEOF_SRVC'))
 ORDER BY
       owner,
       table_name

SELECT owner||'.'||table_name table_name,
       partitioned,
       degree,
       temporary,
       blocks,
       num_rows,
       avg_row_len,
       sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       global_stats,
       compression
  FROM dba_tables
 WHERE (owner, table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','A_LNGSLIST'),('THH_C4C','A_MEMBPCP'),('THH_C4C','A_USR'),('THH_C4C','A_USR_ADD'),('THH_C4C','A_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_A_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_USR'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','T_APBL'),('THH_C4C','T_APL'),('THH_C4C','T_APVLTRKGDEND'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_BLR_PLT'),('THH_C4C','T_CFRDREVW'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCT'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDS'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL_ITEMPVDRSSPS'),('THH_C4C','T_FAX_CSFNCASEPVDR'),('THH_C4C','T_FAX_CSFNRQNGPVDR'),('THH_C4C','T_FRDSAND_FMLYLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_FRTSFDRS'),('THH_C4C','T_GRP_MEMS'),('THH_C4C','T_LCNSLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_LWSTCOSTPVDR'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_ORG_CHRTITEM'),('THH_C4C','T_OTHER_INSURANCE'),('THH_C4C','T_PHI'),('THH_C4C','T_PROVIDER_CHOICE'),('THH_C4C','T_PRSC'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRADVEGRP_PVRS'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRASTN'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRPAYRDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRPLNSAFFS'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDR_DIR_DETAILS'),('THH_C4C','T_SVGSCAT_DTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_SYTMSTNGDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_TAKNASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_TNFRREC'),('THH_C4C','T_UM_CSFNRQNGPVRS'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_ADD'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_GRANT_DGIS_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_GRANT_RESTRICTED_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_WKFWTSK'),('THH_C4C','T_XMPTPVRS'))
 ORDER BY
       owner,
       table_name

DECLARE
  l_pair VARCHAR2(32767);
BEGIN
  DBMS_LOB.CREATETEMPORARY(:tables_list, TRUE, DBMS_LOB.SESSION);
  FOR i IN (WITH object AS (
  	    SELECT /*+ MATERIALIZE */
  	           object_owner owner, object_name name
  	      FROM gv$sql_plan
  	     WHERE inst_id IN (SELECT inst_id FROM gv$instance)
  	       AND sql_id = :sql_id
  	       AND object_owner IS NOT NULL
  	       AND object_name IS NOT NULL
  	     UNION
  	    SELECT object_owner owner, object_name name
  	      FROM dba_hist_sql_plan
  	     WHERE :license = 'Y'
  	       AND dbid = :dbid
  	       AND sql_id = :sql_id
  	       AND object_owner IS NOT NULL
  	       AND object_name IS NOT NULL
  	     UNION
  	    SELECT CASE h.current_obj# WHEN 0 THEN 'SYS' ELSE o.owner END owner,
  	           CASE h.current_obj# WHEN 0 THEN 'UNDO' ELSE o.object_name END name
  	      FROM gv$active_session_history h,
  	           dba_objects o
  	     WHERE :license = 'Y'
  	       AND h.sql_id = :sql_id
  	       AND h.current_obj# >= 0
  	       AND o.object_id(+) = h.current_obj#
  	     UNION
  	    SELECT /*+
               FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn)
               FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash)
               FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)
               USE_HASH(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)
               FULL(h.sn)
               FULL(h.ash)
               FULL(h.evt)
               USE_HASH(h.sn h.ash h.evt)
               */
               CASE h.current_obj# WHEN 0 THEN 'SYS' ELSE o.owner END owner,
  	           CASE h.current_obj# WHEN 0 THEN 'UNDO' ELSE o.object_name END name
  	      FROM dba_hist_active_sess_history h,
  	           dba_objects o
  	     WHERE :license = 'Y'
  	       AND h.dbid = :dbid
  	       AND h.sql_id = :sql_id
  	       AND h.current_obj# >= 0
  	       AND o.object_id(+) = h.current_obj#
  	    )
  	    SELECT 'TABLE', t.owner, t.table_name
  	      FROM dba_tab_statistics t, -- include fixed objects
  	           object o
  	     WHERE t.owner = o.owner
  	       AND t.table_name = o.name
  	     UNION
  	    SELECT 'TABLE', i.table_owner, i.table_name
  	      FROM dba_indexes i,
  	           object o
  	     WHERE i.owner = o.owner
  	       AND i.index_name = o.name)
  LOOP
    IF l_pair IS NULL THEN
      DBMS_LOB.WRITEAPPEND(:tables_list, 1, '(');
    ELSE
      IF DBMS_LOB.GETLENGTH(:tables_list) < 2799 THEN
        DBMS_LOB.WRITEAPPEND(:tables_list, 1, ',');
      END IF;
    END IF;
    l_pair := '('''||i.owner||''','''||i.table_name||''')';
    -- SP2-0341: line overflow during variable substitution (>3000 characters at line 12)
    IF DBMS_LOB.GETLENGTH(:tables_list) < 2800 THEN
      DBMS_LOB.WRITEAPPEND(:tables_list, LENGTH(l_pair), l_pair);
    ELSE
      EXIT;
    END IF;
  END LOOP;
  IF l_pair IS NULL THEN
    l_pair := '((''DUMMY'',''DUMMY''))';
    DBMS_LOB.WRITEAPPEND(:tables_list, LENGTH(l_pair), l_pair);
  ELSE
    DBMS_LOB.WRITEAPPEND(:tables_list, 1, ')');
  END IF;
END;

Execute     18      0.05       0.06          0        886       1898          18
Fetch        0      0.00       0.00          0          0          0           0

Misses in library cache during execute: 1
Optimizer mode: ALL_ROWS
Parsing user id: SYS

WITH
pm AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM gv$sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('0sjx29v99zfqc')
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM dba_hist_sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('0sjx29v99zfqc')
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pm_pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value
 UNION
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
p AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm_pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
phv_perf AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       snap_id,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('0sjx29v99zfqc')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       snap_id ),
phv_stats AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       MAX(avg_et_us) p100_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p99_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p97_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p95_et_us,
       MAX(avg_cpu_us) p100_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p99_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p97_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p95_cpu_us
  FROM phv_perf
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
m AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time)/SUM(executions) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time)/SUM(executions) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets)/SUM(executions)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed)/SUM(executions)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM gv$sql
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('0sjx29v99zfqc')
   AND executions > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
a AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions_delta) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('0sjx29v99zfqc')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value )
SELECT
       p.plan_hash_value,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_mem,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_mem,
       a.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_awr,
       m.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_mem,
       a.avg_rows_processed avg_row_awr,
       m.avg_rows_processed avg_row_mem,
       a.executions executions_awr,
       m.executions executions_mem,
       LEAST(NVL(m.min_cost, a.min_cost), NVL(a.min_cost, m.min_cost)) min_cost,
       GREATEST(NVL(m.max_cost, a.max_cost), NVL(a.max_cost, m.max_cost)) max_cost,
       p.nl,
       p.hj,
       p.mj,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_cpu_ms
  FROM p, m, a, phv_stats s
 WHERE p.plan_hash_value = m.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = a.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = s.plan_hash_value(+)
 ORDER BY
       NVL(a.avg_et_us, m.avg_et_us), m.avg_et_us

call     count       cpu    elapsed       disk      query    current        rows

Parse        1      0.00       0.00          0          0          0           0

Fetch        3      0.01       0.02          0          0          0          24
------- ------  -------- ---------- ---------- ---------- ----------  ----------
total        5      0.02       0.06          0          0          0          24

Misses in library cache during parse: 1
Misses in library cache during execute: 1

WITH
pm AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM gv$sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('gczs60dfwg9gm')
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM dba_hist_sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('gczs60dfwg9gm')
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pm_pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value
 UNION
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
p AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm_pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
phv_perf AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       snap_id,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('gczs60dfwg9gm')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       snap_id ),
phv_stats AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       MAX(avg_et_us) p100_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p99_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p97_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p95_et_us,
       MAX(avg_cpu_us) p100_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p99_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p97_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p95_cpu_us
  FROM phv_perf
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
m AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time)/SUM(executions) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time)/SUM(executions) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets)/SUM(executions)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed)/SUM(executions)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM gv$sql
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('gczs60dfwg9gm')
   AND executions > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
a AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions_delta) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('gczs60dfwg9gm')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value )
SELECT
       p.plan_hash_value,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_mem,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_mem,
       a.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_awr,
       m.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_mem,
       a.avg_rows_processed avg_row_awr,
       m.avg_rows_processed avg_row_mem,
       a.executions executions_awr,
       m.executions executions_mem,
       LEAST(NVL(m.min_cost, a.min_cost), NVL(a.min_cost, m.min_cost)) min_cost,
       GREATEST(NVL(m.max_cost, a.max_cost), NVL(a.max_cost, m.max_cost)) max_cost,
       p.nl,
       p.hj,
       p.mj,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_cpu_ms
  FROM p, m, a, phv_stats s
 WHERE p.plan_hash_value = m.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = a.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = s.plan_hash_value(+)
 ORDER BY
       NVL(a.avg_et_us, m.avg_et_us), m.avg_et_us

call     count       cpu    elapsed       disk      query    current        rows
------- ------  -------- ---------- ---------- ---------- ----------  ----------
Parse        1      0.00       0.00          0          0          0           0

Fetch        2      0.01       0.01          0          0          0           1

SELECT owner||'.'||table_name table_name,
       partitioned,
       degree,
       temporary,
       blocks,
       num_rows,
       avg_row_len,
       sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       global_stats,
       compression
  FROM dba_tables
 WHERE (owner, table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','A_LNGSLIST'),('THH_C4C','A_MEMBPCP'),('THH_C4C','A_USR'),('THH_C4C','A_USR_ADD'),('THH_C4C','A_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_A_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_USR'),('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','T_APBL'),('THH_C4C','T_APL'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER'),('THH_C4C','T_BARRIER_TEMPLATE'),('THH_C4C','T_BLR_PLT'),('THH_C4C','T_CFRDREVW'),('THH_C4C','T_CNCT'),('THH_C4C','T_CSTMFLDS'),('THH_C4C','T_DDL_ITEMPVDRSSPS'),('THH_C4C','T_FAX_CSFNCASEPVDR'),('THH_C4C','T_FAX_CSFNRQNGPVDR'),('THH_C4C','T_FRDSAND_FMLYLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_FRTSFDRS'),('THH_C4C','T_GRP_MEMS'),('THH_C4C','T_LCNSLIST'),('THH_C4C','T_LWSTCOSTPVDR'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','T_MEMBDGISBASE'),('THH_C4C','T_ORG_CHRTITEM'),('THH_C4C','T_OTHER_INSURANCE'),('THH_C4C','T_PHI'),('THH_C4C','T_PROVIDER_CHOICE'),('THH_C4C','T_PRSC'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRADVEGRP_PVRS'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRASTN'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRPAYRDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDRPLNSAFFS'),('THH_C4C','T_PVDR_DIR_DETAILS'),('THH_C4C','T_SVGSCAT_DTLS'),('THH_C4C','T_SYTMSTNGDAT'),('THH_C4C','T_TAKNASMTCC_BASE'),('THH_C4C','T_TNFRREC'),('THH_C4C','T_UM_CSFNRQNGPVRS'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_ADD'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_GRANT_DGIS_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_USR_GRANT_RESTRICTED_XREF'),('THH_C4C','T_WKFWTSK'),('THH_C4C','T_XMPTPVRS'))
 ORDER BY

       table_name

SELECT EXTRACTVALUE(VALUE(T), '/u') 
FROM
 TABLE(XMLSEQUENCE(EXTRACT(XMLTYPE(:B1 ), '/*/spd/u'))) T

WITH
pm AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM gv$sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('1wjt2ut7cah6k')
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM dba_hist_sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('1wjt2ut7cah6k')
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pm_pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value
 UNION
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
p AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm_pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
phv_perf AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       snap_id,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('1wjt2ut7cah6k')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       snap_id ),
phv_stats AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       MAX(avg_et_us) p100_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p99_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p97_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p95_et_us,
       MAX(avg_cpu_us) p100_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p99_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p97_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p95_cpu_us
  FROM phv_perf
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
m AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time)/SUM(executions) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time)/SUM(executions) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets)/SUM(executions)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed)/SUM(executions)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM gv$sql
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('1wjt2ut7cah6k')
   AND executions > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
a AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions_delta) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('1wjt2ut7cah6k')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value )
SELECT
       p.plan_hash_value,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_mem,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_mem,
       a.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_awr,
       m.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_mem,
       a.avg_rows_processed avg_row_awr,
       m.avg_rows_processed avg_row_mem,
       a.executions executions_awr,
       m.executions executions_mem,
       LEAST(NVL(m.min_cost, a.min_cost), NVL(a.min_cost, m.min_cost)) min_cost,
       GREATEST(NVL(m.max_cost, a.max_cost), NVL(a.max_cost, m.max_cost)) max_cost,
       p.nl,
       p.hj,
       p.mj,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_cpu_ms
  FROM p, m, a, phv_stats s
 WHERE p.plan_hash_value = m.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = a.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = s.plan_hash_value(+)
 ORDER BY
       NVL(a.avg_et_us, m.avg_et_us), m.avg_et_us

call     count       cpu    elapsed       disk      query    current        rows
------- ------  -------- ---------- ---------- ---------- ----------  ----------
Parse        1      0.00       0.00          0          0          0           0
Execute      1      0.01       0.04          0          0          0           0
Fetch        2      0.00       0.01          0          0          0           1
------- ------  -------- ---------- ---------- ---------- ----------  ----------
total        4      0.02       0.06          0          0          0           1

       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM dba_hist_sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('brg5vk35jcqtv')
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pm_pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value
 UNION
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
p AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm_pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
phv_perf AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       snap_id,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('brg5vk35jcqtv')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       snap_id ),
phv_stats AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       MAX(avg_et_us) p100_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p99_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p97_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p95_et_us,
       MAX(avg_cpu_us) p100_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p99_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p97_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p95_cpu_us
  FROM phv_perf
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
m AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time)/SUM(executions) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time)/SUM(executions) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets)/SUM(executions)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed)/SUM(executions)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM gv$sql
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('brg5vk35jcqtv')
   AND executions > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
a AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions_delta) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('brg5vk35jcqtv')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value )
SELECT
       p.plan_hash_value,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_mem,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_mem,
       a.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_awr,
       m.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_mem,
       a.avg_rows_processed avg_row_awr,
       m.avg_rows_processed avg_row_mem,
       a.executions executions_awr,
       m.executions executions_mem,
       LEAST(NVL(m.min_cost, a.min_cost), NVL(a.min_cost, m.min_cost)) min_cost,
       GREATEST(NVL(m.max_cost, a.max_cost), NVL(a.max_cost, m.max_cost)) max_cost,
       p.nl,
       p.hj,
       p.mj,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_cpu_ms
  FROM p, m, a, phv_stats s
 WHERE p.plan_hash_value = m.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = a.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = s.plan_hash_value(+)
 ORDER BY
       NVL(a.avg_et_us, m.avg_et_us), m.avg_et_us

SELECT i.table_owner||'.'||i.table_name||' '||i.owner||'.'||i.index_name table_and_index_name,
       i.partitioned,
       i.degree,
       i.index_type,
       i.uniqueness,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM dba_ind_columns ic WHERE ic.index_owner = i.owner AND ic.index_name = i.index_name) columns,
       i.status,
       i.visibility,
       i.blevel,
       i.leaf_blocks,
       i.distinct_keys,
       i.clustering_factor,
       i.num_rows,
       i.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(i.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       i.global_stats
  FROM dba_indexes i
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','MV_PATID_THRESH_COND_CLAIM'),('THH_C4C','T_DRUGCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCLCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'))
 ORDER BY
       i.table_owner,
       i.table_name,
       i.owner,
       i.index_name

        11         16         20  SORT ORDER BY (cr=4 pr=1 pw=0 time=426 us cost=0 size=0 card=0)
        11         16         20   TABLE ACCESS CLUSTER HISTGRM$ (cr=4 pr=1 pw=0 time=394 us)
         1          1          1    INDEX UNIQUE SCAN I_OBJ#_INTCOL# (cr=2 pr=0 pw=0 time=7 us)(object id 65)

WITH
pm AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM gv$sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('0g2sz99zbn7ur')
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM dba_hist_sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('0g2sz99zbn7ur')
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pm_pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value
 UNION
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
p AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm_pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
phv_perf AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       snap_id,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('0g2sz99zbn7ur')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       snap_id ),
phv_stats AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       MAX(avg_et_us) p100_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p99_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p97_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p95_et_us,
       MAX(avg_cpu_us) p100_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p99_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p97_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p95_cpu_us
  FROM phv_perf
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
m AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time)/SUM(executions) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time)/SUM(executions) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets)/SUM(executions)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed)/SUM(executions)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM gv$sql
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('0g2sz99zbn7ur')
   AND executions > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
a AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions_delta) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('0g2sz99zbn7ur')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value )
SELECT
       p.plan_hash_value,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_mem,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_mem,
       a.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_awr,
       m.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_mem,
       a.avg_rows_processed avg_row_awr,
       m.avg_rows_processed avg_row_mem,
       a.executions executions_awr,
       m.executions executions_mem,
       LEAST(NVL(m.min_cost, a.min_cost), NVL(a.min_cost, m.min_cost)) min_cost,
       GREATEST(NVL(m.max_cost, a.max_cost), NVL(a.max_cost, m.max_cost)) max_cost,
       p.nl,
       p.hj,
       p.mj,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_cpu_ms
  FROM p, m, a, phv_stats s
 WHERE p.plan_hash_value = m.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = a.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = s.plan_hash_value(+)
 ORDER BY
       NVL(a.avg_et_us, m.avg_et_us), m.avg_et_us

WITH
pm AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM gv$sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('bzsm5n1q7g4z6')
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM dba_hist_sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('bzsm5n1q7g4z6')
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pm_pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value
 UNION
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
p AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm_pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
phv_perf AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       snap_id,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('bzsm5n1q7g4z6')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       snap_id ),
phv_stats AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       MAX(avg_et_us) p100_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p99_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p97_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p95_et_us,
       MAX(avg_cpu_us) p100_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p99_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p97_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p95_cpu_us
  FROM phv_perf
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
m AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time)/SUM(executions) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time)/SUM(executions) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets)/SUM(executions)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed)/SUM(executions)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM gv$sql
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('bzsm5n1q7g4z6')
   AND executions > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
a AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions_delta) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('bzsm5n1q7g4z6')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value )
SELECT
       p.plan_hash_value,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_mem,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_mem,
       a.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_awr,
       m.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_mem,
       a.avg_rows_processed avg_row_awr,
       m.avg_rows_processed avg_row_mem,
       a.executions executions_awr,
       m.executions executions_mem,
       LEAST(NVL(m.min_cost, a.min_cost), NVL(a.min_cost, m.min_cost)) min_cost,
       GREATEST(NVL(m.max_cost, a.max_cost), NVL(a.max_cost, m.max_cost)) max_cost,
       p.nl,
       p.hj,
       p.mj,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_cpu_ms
  FROM p, m, a, phv_stats s
 WHERE p.plan_hash_value = m.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = a.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = s.plan_hash_value(+)
 ORDER BY
       NVL(a.avg_et_us, m.avg_et_us), m.avg_et_us

SELECT i.table_owner||'.'||i.table_name||' '||i.owner||'.'||i.index_name table_and_index_name,
       i.partitioned,
       i.degree,
       i.index_type,
       i.uniqueness,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM dba_ind_columns ic WHERE ic.index_owner = i.owner AND ic.index_name = i.index_name) columns,
       i.status,
       i.visibility,
       i.blevel,
       i.leaf_blocks,
       i.distinct_keys,
       i.clustering_factor,
       i.num_rows,
       i.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(i.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       i.global_stats
  FROM dba_indexes i
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','A_USR_ADD'),('THH_C4C','A_USR_CNCTINFO'),('THH_C4C','MV_DIM_MEMBER_ADDR_TMPRL'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'))
 ORDER BY
       i.table_owner,
       i.table_name,
       i.owner,
       i.index_name

WITH
pm AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM gv$sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('00540ttuxh7n9')
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM dba_hist_sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('00540ttuxh7n9')
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pm_pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value
 UNION
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
p AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm_pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
phv_perf AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       snap_id,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('00540ttuxh7n9')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       snap_id ),
phv_stats AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       MAX(avg_et_us) p100_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p99_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p97_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p95_et_us,
       MAX(avg_cpu_us) p100_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p99_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p97_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p95_cpu_us
  FROM phv_perf
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
m AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time)/SUM(executions) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time)/SUM(executions) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets)/SUM(executions)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed)/SUM(executions)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM gv$sql
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('00540ttuxh7n9')
   AND executions > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
a AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions_delta) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('00540ttuxh7n9')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value )
SELECT
       p.plan_hash_value,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_mem,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_mem,
       a.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_awr,
       m.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_mem,
       a.avg_rows_processed avg_row_awr,
       m.avg_rows_processed avg_row_mem,
       a.executions executions_awr,
       m.executions executions_mem,
       LEAST(NVL(m.min_cost, a.min_cost), NVL(a.min_cost, m.min_cost)) min_cost,
       GREATEST(NVL(m.max_cost, a.max_cost), NVL(a.max_cost, m.max_cost)) max_cost,
       p.nl,
       p.hj,
       p.mj,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_cpu_ms
  FROM p, m, a, phv_stats s
 WHERE p.plan_hash_value = m.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = a.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = s.plan_hash_value(+)
 ORDER BY
       NVL(a.avg_et_us, m.avg_et_us), m.avg_et_us

SELECT /*+ RESULT_CACHE (SYSOBJ=TRUE) */ DBID,SQL_ID,SQL_TEXT,COMMAND_TYPE,
  CON_ID 
FROM
 "SYS"."INT$DBA_HIST_SQLTEXT" "INT$DBA_HIST_SQLTEXT" WHERE 
  ("INT$DBA_HIST_SQLTEXT"."CON_ID"=0 OR "INT$DBA_HIST_SQLTEXT"."CON_ID"=4) 
  AND ("INT$DBA_HIST_SQLTEXT".CON_ID=0 OR "INT$DBA_HIST_SQLTEXT".CON_ID=4)
