WITH
pm AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM gv$sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('2mrjsarqc32h3')
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM dba_hist_sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('2mrjsarqc32h3')
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pm_pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value
 UNION
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
p AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm_pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
phv_perf AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       snap_id,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('2mrjsarqc32h3')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       snap_id ),
phv_stats AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       MAX(avg_et_us) p100_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p99_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p97_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p95_et_us,
       MAX(avg_cpu_us) p100_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p99_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p97_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p95_cpu_us
  FROM phv_perf
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
m AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time)/SUM(executions) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time)/SUM(executions) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets)/SUM(executions)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed)/SUM(executions)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM gv$sql
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('2mrjsarqc32h3')
   AND executions > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
a AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions_delta) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('2mrjsarqc32h3')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value )
SELECT
       p.plan_hash_value,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_mem,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_mem,
       a.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_awr,
       m.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_mem,
       a.avg_rows_processed avg_row_awr,
       m.avg_rows_processed avg_row_mem,
       a.executions executions_awr,
       m.executions executions_mem,
       LEAST(NVL(m.min_cost, a.min_cost), NVL(a.min_cost, m.min_cost)) min_cost,
       GREATEST(NVL(m.max_cost, a.max_cost), NVL(a.max_cost, m.max_cost)) max_cost,
       p.nl,
       p.hj,
       p.mj,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_cpu_ms
  FROM p, m, a, phv_stats s
 WHERE p.plan_hash_value = m.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = a.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = s.plan_hash_value(+)
 ORDER BY
       NVL(a.avg_et_us, m.avg_et_us), m.avg_et_us

WITH
pm AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM gv$sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('17vjd1aast5q7')
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM dba_hist_sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('17vjd1aast5q7')
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pm_pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value
 UNION
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
p AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm_pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
phv_perf AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       snap_id,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('17vjd1aast5q7')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       snap_id ),
phv_stats AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       MAX(avg_et_us) p100_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p99_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p97_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p95_et_us,
       MAX(avg_cpu_us) p100_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p99_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p97_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p95_cpu_us
  FROM phv_perf
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
m AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time)/SUM(executions) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time)/SUM(executions) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets)/SUM(executions)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed)/SUM(executions)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM gv$sql
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('17vjd1aast5q7')
   AND executions > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
a AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions_delta) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('17vjd1aast5q7')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value )
SELECT
       p.plan_hash_value,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_mem,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_mem,
       a.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_awr,
       m.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_mem,
       a.avg_rows_processed avg_row_awr,
       m.avg_rows_processed avg_row_mem,
       a.executions executions_awr,
       m.executions executions_mem,
       LEAST(NVL(m.min_cost, a.min_cost), NVL(a.min_cost, m.min_cost)) min_cost,
       GREATEST(NVL(m.max_cost, a.max_cost), NVL(a.max_cost, m.max_cost)) max_cost,
       p.nl,
       p.hj,
       p.mj,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_cpu_ms
  FROM p, m, a, phv_stats s
 WHERE p.plan_hash_value = m.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = a.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = s.plan_hash_value(+)
 ORDER BY
       NVL(a.avg_et_us, m.avg_et_us), m.avg_et_us

WITH
pm AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM gv$sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('cydgfyx406q8j')
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM dba_hist_sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('cydgfyx406q8j')
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pm_pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value
 UNION
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
p AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm_pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
phv_perf AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       snap_id,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('cydgfyx406q8j')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       snap_id ),
phv_stats AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       MAX(avg_et_us) p100_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p99_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p97_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p95_et_us,
       MAX(avg_cpu_us) p100_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p99_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p97_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p95_cpu_us
  FROM phv_perf
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
m AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time)/SUM(executions) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time)/SUM(executions) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets)/SUM(executions)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed)/SUM(executions)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM gv$sql
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('cydgfyx406q8j')
   AND executions > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
a AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions_delta) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('cydgfyx406q8j')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value )
SELECT
       p.plan_hash_value,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_mem,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_mem,
       a.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_awr,
       m.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_mem,
       a.avg_rows_processed avg_row_awr,
       m.avg_rows_processed avg_row_mem,
       a.executions executions_awr,
       m.executions executions_mem,
       LEAST(NVL(m.min_cost, a.min_cost), NVL(a.min_cost, m.min_cost)) min_cost,
       GREATEST(NVL(m.max_cost, a.max_cost), NVL(a.max_cost, m.max_cost)) max_cost,
       p.nl,
       p.hj,
       p.mj,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_cpu_ms
  FROM p, m, a, phv_stats s
 WHERE p.plan_hash_value = m.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = a.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = s.plan_hash_value(+)
 ORDER BY
       NVL(a.avg_et_us, m.avg_et_us), m.avg_et_us

       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_mem,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_mem,
       a.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_awr,
       m.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_mem,
       a.avg_rows_processed avg_row_awr,
       m.avg_rows_processed avg_row_mem,
       a.executions executions_awr,
       m.executions executions_mem,
       LEAST(NVL(m.min_cost, a.min_cost), NVL(a.min_cost, m.min_cost)) min_cost,
       GREATEST(NVL(m.max_cost, a.max_cost), NVL(a.max_cost, m.max_cost)) max_cost,
       p.nl,
       p.hj,
       p.mj,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_cpu_ms
  FROM p, m, a, phv_stats s
 WHERE p.plan_hash_value = m.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = a.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = s.plan_hash_value(+)
 ORDER BY
       NVL(a.avg_et_us, m.avg_et_us), m.avg_et_us

SELECT i.table_owner||'.'||i.table_name||' '||i.owner||'.'||i.index_name table_and_index_name,
       i.partitioned,
       i.degree,
       i.index_type,
       i.uniqueness,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM dba_ind_columns ic WHERE ic.index_owner = i.owner AND ic.index_name = i.index_name) columns,
       i.status,
       i.visibility,
       i.blevel,
       i.leaf_blocks,
       i.distinct_keys,
       i.clustering_factor,
       i.num_rows,
       i.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(i.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       i.global_stats
  FROM dba_indexes i
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('SYS','ACLMVREFSTAT$'),('THH_C4C','MV_DIM_CLAIM'),('THH_C4C','T_DGIS'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCLCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_PLCEOF_SRVC'))
 ORDER BY
       i.table_owner,
       i.table_name,
       i.owner,
       i.index_name

SELECT i.table_owner||'.'||i.table_name||' '||i.owner||'.'||i.index_name table_and_index_name,
       i.partitioned,
       i.degree,
       i.index_type,
       i.uniqueness,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM dba_ind_columns ic WHERE ic.index_owner = i.owner AND ic.index_name = i.index_name) columns,
       i.status,

       i.distinct_keys,
       i.clustering_factor,

SELECT i.table_owner||'.'||i.table_name||' '||i.owner||'.'||i.index_name table_and_index_name,
       i.partitioned,
       i.degree,
       i.index_type,
       i.uniqueness,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM dba_ind_columns ic WHERE ic.index_owner = i.owner AND ic.index_name = i.index_name) columns,
       i.status,
       i.visibility,
       i.blevel,
       i.leaf_blocks,
       i.distinct_keys,
       i.clustering_factor,
       i.num_rows,
       i.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(i.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       i.global_stats
  FROM dba_indexes i
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','T_DDL_ITEM'),('THH_C4C','T_NOTE'),('THH_C4C_DW','DW_DIM_NOTE'),('THH_C4C_DW','RPT_CONSTANTS'))
 ORDER BY
       i.table_owner,
       i.table_name,
       i.owner,
       i.index_name

DECLARE
  l_count NUMBER := 0;
  CURSOR sql_cur IS
              WITH ranked_sql AS (
            SELECT /*+  DYNAMIC_SAMPLING(4)   FULL(h.ash) FULL(h.evt) FULL(h.sn) USE_HASH(h.sn h.ash h.evt)   FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn) FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash) FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)   USE_HASH(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)  *//* MATERIALIZE NO_MERGE */
                   /* 7b.1045 */
                   con_id,
                   dbid,
                   sql_id,
                   MAX(user_id) user_id,
                   MAX(module) module,
                   ROUND(COUNT(*) / 360, 6) db_time_hrs,
                   ROUND(SUM(CASE session_state WHEN 'ON CPU' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / 360, 6) cpu_time_hrs,
                   ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN session_state = 'WAITING' AND wait_class IN ('User I/O', 'System I/O') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / 360, 6) io_time_hrs,
                   ROW_NUMBER () OVER (ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC) rank_num
              FROM dba_hist_active_sess_history h
             WHERE sql_id IS NOT NULL
               AND snap_id BETWEEN 3473 AND 4962
               AND dbid = 2109323688
               AND '' IS NULL
             GROUP BY
                   con_id,
                   dbid,
                   sql_id
            HAVING COUNT(*) > 60 -- >10min
            ),
            top_sql AS (
            SELECT /*+  MATERIALIZE NO_MERGE  7b.1045 */
                   r.con_id,
                   r.sql_id,
                   TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(r.db_time_hrs, 2), '99990.00')) db_time_hrs,
                   TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(r.cpu_time_hrs, 2), '99990.00')) cpu_time_hrs,
                   TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(r.io_time_hrs, 2), '99990.00')) io_time_hrs,
                   r.rank_num,
                   NVL((SELECT a.name FROM audit_actions a WHERE a.action = h.command_type), TO_CHAR(h.command_type)) command_type,
                   NVL((SELECT u.username FROM dba_users u WHERE u.user_id = r.user_id), TO_CHAR(r.user_id)) username,
                   r.module,
                   --h.sql_text,
                   CASE
                   WHEN h.sql_text IS NULL THEN 'unknown'
                   ELSE REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(DBMS_LOB.SUBSTR(h.sql_text, 1000), CHR(10), ' '), '"', CHR(38)||'#34;'), '>', CHR(38)||'#62;'), '<', CHR(38)||'#60;')
                   END sql_text_1000
              FROM ranked_sql r,
                   dba_hist_sqltext h
             WHERE r.rank_num <= 16
               AND h.con_id(+) = r.con_id
               AND h.dbid(+) = r.dbid
               AND h.sql_id(+) = r.sql_id
            ),
            not_shared AS (
            SELECT /*+ 7b.1045 *//* MATERIALIZE NO_MERGE */
                   con_id,
                   sql_id, COUNT(*) child_cursors,
                   RANK() OVER (ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC NULLS LAST) AS sql_rank
              FROM gv$sql_shared_cursor
             WHERE sql_id NOT IN (SELECT sql_id FROM top_sql)
             GROUP BY
                   con_id,
                   sql_id
            HAVING COUNT(*) > 100
            ),
            top_not_shared AS (
            SELECT /*+  MATERIALIZE NO_MERGE  7b.1045 */
                   DISTINCT
                   ns.sql_rank,
                   ns.child_cursors,
                   ns.con_id,
                   ns.sql_id,
                   REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(DBMS_LOB.SUBSTR(s.sql_fulltext, 1000), CHR(10), ' '), '"', CHR(38)||'#34;'), '>', CHR(38)||'#62;'), '<', CHR(38)||'#60;') sql_text_1000
              FROM not_shared ns, gv$sql s
             WHERE s.sql_id(+) = ns.sql_id
               AND s.con_id(+) = ns.con_id
               AND ns.sql_rank <= 2
            ),
            by_signature AS (
            SELECT /*+ FULL(ts) FULL(ns) USE_HASH(ts ns h)  MATERIALIZE NO_MERGE   DYNAMIC_SAMPLING(4)   FULL(h.ash) FULL(h.evt) FULL(h.sn) USE_HASH(h.sn h.ash h.evt)   FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn) FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash) FULL(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)   USE_HASH(h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.sn h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.ash h.INT$DBA_HIST_ACT_SESS_HISTORY.evt)  */
                   /* 7b.1045 */
                   h.con_id,
                   h.force_matching_signature,
                   h.dbid,
                   ROW_NUMBER () OVER (ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC) rn,
                   COUNT(DISTINCT h.sql_id) distinct_sql_id,
                   MIN(h.sql_id) sample_sql_id,
                   COUNT(*) samples
              FROM dba_hist_active_sess_history h,
                   top_sql ts,
                   top_not_shared ns
             WHERE h.sql_id IS NOT NULL
               AND h.force_matching_signature IS NOT NULL
               AND h.snap_id BETWEEN 3473 AND 4962
               AND h.dbid = 2109323688
               AND h.sql_id = ts.sql_id(+)
               AND h.con_id = ts.con_id(+)
               AND h.sql_id = ns.sql_id(+)
               AND h.con_id = ns.con_id(+)
               AND ts.sql_id(+) IS NULL
               AND ns.sql_id(+) IS NULL
               AND '' IS NULL
             GROUP BY
                   h.con_id,
                   h.force_matching_signature,
                   h.dbid
            HAVING COUNT(*) > 60 -- >10min
            ),
            top_signature AS (
            SELECT /*+  MATERIALIZE NO_MERGE  7b.1045 */
                   r.rn,
                   r.con_id,
                   r.force_matching_signature,
                   r.distinct_sql_id,
                   r.sample_sql_id,
                   r.samples,
                   CASE
                   WHEN h.sql_text IS NULL THEN 'unknown'
                   ELSE REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(DBMS_LOB.SUBSTR(h.sql_text, 1000), CHR(10), ' '), '"', CHR(38)||'#34;'), '>', CHR(38)||'#62;'), '<', CHR(38)||'#60;')
                   END sql_text_1000
              FROM by_signature r,
                   dba_hist_sqltext h
             WHERE r.rn <= 2
               AND h.con_id(+) = r.con_id
               AND h.dbid(+) = r.dbid
               AND h.sql_id(+) = r.sample_sql_id
            )
            SELECT rank_num,
                   con_id,
                    -- skip 12c TO_NUMBER(NULL) con_id,
                   (SELECT pd.pdb_name FROM dba_pdbs pd WHERE pd.con_id = ts.con_id) pdb_name,
                    -- skip 12c NULL pdb_name,
                   sql_id,
                   db_time_hrs, -- not null means Top as per DB time
                   cpu_time_hrs, -- not null means Top as per DB time
                   io_time_hrs, -- not null means Top as per DB time
                   command_type, -- not null means Top as per DB time
                   username, -- not null means Top as per DB time
                   module, -- not null means Top as per DB time
                   sql_text_1000,
                   1 top_type, -- as per DB time
                   0 child_cursors, -- <> 0 means Top as per number of cursors
                   0 signature, -- <> 0 means Top as per signature
                   0 distinct_sql_id -- <> 0 means Top as per signature
              FROM top_sql ts
             UNION ALL
            SELECT sql_rank rank_num,
                   con_id,
                    -- skip 12c TO_NUMBER(NULL) con_id,
                   (SELECT pd.pdb_name FROM dba_pdbs pd WHERE pd.con_id = ns.con_id) pdb_name,
                    -- skip 12c NULL pdb_name,
                   sql_id,
                   NULL db_time_hrs, -- not null means Top as per DB time
                   NULL cpu_time_hrs, -- not null means Top as per DB time
                   NULL io_time_hrs, -- not null means Top as per DB time
                   NULL command_type, -- not null means Top as per DB time
                   NULL username, -- not null means Top as per DB time
                   NULL module, -- not null means Top as per DB time
                   --sql_text sql_text_1000,
                   sql_text_1000,
                   2 top_type, -- as per not shared cursors
                   child_cursors, -- <> 0 means Top as per number of cursors
                   0 signature, -- <> 0 means Top as per signature
                   0 distinct_sql_id -- <> 0 means Top as per signature
              FROM top_not_shared ns
             UNION ALL
            SELECT rn rank_num,
                   con_id,
                    -- skip 12c TO_NUMBER(NULL) con_id,
                   (SELECT pd.pdb_name FROM dba_pdbs pd WHERE pd.con_id = ts.con_id) pdb_name,
                    -- skip 12c NULL pdb_name,
                   sample_sql_id sql_id,
                   NULL db_time_hrs, -- not null means Top as per DB time
                   NULL cpu_time_hrs, -- not null means Top as per DB time
                   NULL io_time_hrs, -- not null means Top as per DB time
                   NULL command_type, -- not null means Top as per DB time
                   NULL username, -- not null means Top as per DB time
                   NULL module, -- not null means Top as per DB time
                   sql_text_1000,
                   3 top_type, -- as per force matching signature
                   0 child_cursors, -- <> 0 means Top as per number of cursors
                   force_matching_signature signature, -- <> 0 means Top as per signature
                   distinct_sql_id -- <> 0 means Top as per signature
              FROM top_signature ts
              ORDER BY 1, 10, 3 DESC, 2;
  sql_rec sql_cur%ROWTYPE;
  PROCEDURE put_line(p_line IN VARCHAR2) IS
  BEGIN
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE(p_line);
  END put_line;
  PROCEDURE update_log(p_module IN VARCHAR2) IS
  BEGIN
    put_line('COL hh_mm_ss NEW_V hh_mm_ss NOPRI FOR A8;');
    put_line('SELECT TO_CHAR(SYSDATE, ''HH24:MI:SS'') hh_mm_ss FROM DUAL;');
    put_line('PRO PRO update log');
    put_line('SPO 00002_edb360_323688_log.txt APP;');
    put_line('SET HEAD OFF TERM ON;');
    put_line('PRO '||CHR(38)||chr(38)||'hh_mm_ss. '||p_module);
    put_line('SELECT ''Elapsed Hours so far: ''||ROUND((DBMS_UTILITY.GET_TIME - :edb360_time0) / 100 / 3600, 3) FROM DUAL;');
    put_line('SET HEAD ON TERM OFF;');
    put_line('SPO OFF;');
  END update_log;
BEGIN
  OPEN sql_cur;
  LOOP
    FETCH sql_cur INTO sql_rec;
    EXIT WHEN sql_cur%NOTFOUND;
    put_line('COL hh_mm_ss NEW_V hh_mm_ss NOPRI FOR A8;');
    put_line('SELECT TO_CHAR(SYSDATE, ''HH24:MI:SS'') hh_mm_ss FROM DUAL;');
    put_line('PRO PRO update log');
    put_line('SPO 00002_edb360_323688_log.txt APP;');
    put_line('PRO');
    put_line('PRO PRO ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~');
    put_line('PRO');
    put_line('PRO rank:'||sql_rec.rank_num||' sql_id:'||sql_rec.sql_id);
    put_line('SPO OFF;');
    put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00002_edb360_323688_log.txt >> 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
    put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
    put_line('PRO PRO update main report1');
    put_line('SPO 00001_edb360_323688_index.html APP;');
    put_line('PRO <li title="pdb:'||sql_rec.pdb_name||' user:'||sql_rec.username||' module:'||sql_rec.module);
    put_line('PRO '||sql_rec.sql_text_1000||'">');
    IF sql_rec.top_type = 1 THEN
      put_line('PRO rank:'||sql_rec.rank_num||' '||sql_rec.sql_id||' et:'||sql_rec.db_time_hrs||'h cpu:'||sql_rec.cpu_time_hrs||'h io:'||sql_rec.io_time_hrs||'h type:'||SUBSTR(sql_rec.command_type, 1, 6));
    ELSIF sql_rec.top_type = 2 THEN
      put_line('PRO rank:'||sql_rec.rank_num||' '||sql_rec.sql_id||' cursors:'||sql_rec.child_cursors);
    ELSIF sql_rec.top_type = 3 THEN
      put_line('PRO rank:'||sql_rec.rank_num||' '||sql_rec.sql_id||' signature:'||sql_rec.signature||'('||sql_rec.distinct_sql_id||')');
    END IF;
    put_line('SET HEAD OFF VER OFF FEED OFF ECHO OFF;');
    put_line('SELECT ''*** time limit exceeded ***'' FROM DUAL WHERE '''||CHR(38)||CHR(38)||'edb360_bypass.'' IS NOT NULL;');
    put_line('SPO OFF;');
    put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00001_edb360_323688_index.html >> 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
    put_line('EXEC :repo_seq := :repo_seq + 1;');
    put_line('SELECT TO_CHAR(:repo_seq) report_sequence FROM DUAL;');
    IF '12.1.0.2.0' >= '12' AND sql_rec.pdb_name IS NOT NULL THEN
      put_line('SPO 00002_edb360_323688_log.txt APP;');
      put_line('PRO PRO ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~');
      put_line('PRO PRO changes PDB to '||sql_rec.pdb_name);
      put_line('ALTER SESSION SET CONTAINER = '||sql_rec.pdb_name||';');
      put_line('PRO PRO ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~');
      put_line('SPO OFF;');
      put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00002_edb360_323688_log.txt >> 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
      put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
    END IF;
    IF sql_rec.rank_num <= 16 AND '' IS NULL THEN
      put_line('COL edb360_bypass NEW_V edb360_bypass;');
      put_line('SELECT '' echo timeout '' edb360_bypass FROM DUAL WHERE (DBMS_UTILITY.GET_TIME - :edb360_time0) / 100  >  :edb360_max_seconds;');
      update_log('PLANX rank:'||sql_rec.rank_num||' SQL_ID:'||sql_rec.sql_id||' TOP_type:'||sql_rec.top_type);
      put_line('@@'||CHR(38)||CHR(38)||'edb360_bypass.sql/planx.sql Y '||sql_rec.sql_id);
      put_line('PRO PRO update main report2');
      put_line('SPO 00001_edb360_323688_index.html APP;');
      put_line('PRO <a href="planx_'||sql_rec.sql_id||'_'||CHR(38)||chr(38)||'current_time..txt">planx(text)</a>');
      put_line('SPO OFF;');
      put_line('PRO PRO zip');
      put_line('HOS zip -mj edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 planx_'||sql_rec.sql_id||'_'||CHR(38)||chr(38)||'current_time..txt >> 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
      put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00001_edb360_323688_index.html >> 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
    END IF;
    IF sql_rec.rank_num <= 0 AND '' IS NULL AND '' IS NULL AND '' IS NULL AND '' IS NULL THEN
      put_line('COL edb360_bypass NEW_V edb360_bypass;');
      put_line('SELECT '' echo timeout '' edb360_bypass FROM DUAL WHERE (DBMS_UTILITY.GET_TIME - :edb360_time0) / 100  >  :edb360_max_seconds;');
      update_log('SQLMON rank:'||sql_rec.rank_num||' SQL_ID:'||sql_rec.sql_id||' TOP_type:'||sql_rec.top_type);
      put_line('@@'||CHR(38)||CHR(38)||'edb360_bypass.sql/sqlmon.sql Y '||sql_rec.sql_id);
      put_line('PRO PRO update main report3');
      put_line('SPO 00001_edb360_323688_index.html APP;');
      put_line('PRO <a href="sqlmon_'||sql_rec.sql_id||'_'||CHR(38)||chr(38)||'current_time..zip">sqlmon(zip)</a>');
      put_line('SPO OFF;');
      put_line('PRO PRO zip');
      put_line('HOS zip -mj edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 sqlmon_'||sql_rec.sql_id||'_'||CHR(38)||chr(38)||'current_time..zip >> 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
      put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00001_edb360_323688_index.html >> 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
    END IF;
    IF sql_rec.rank_num <= 0 AND '' IS NULL AND '' IS NULL THEN
      put_line('COL edb360_bypass NEW_V edb360_bypass;');
      put_line('SELECT '' echo timeout '' edb360_bypass FROM DUAL WHERE (DBMS_UTILITY.GET_TIME - :edb360_time0) / 100  >  :edb360_max_seconds;');
      update_log('SQLASH rank:'||sql_rec.rank_num||' SQL_ID:'||sql_rec.sql_id||' TOP_type:'||sql_rec.top_type);
      put_line('@@'||CHR(38)||CHR(38)||'edb360_bypass.sql/sqlash.sql Y '||sql_rec.sql_id);
      put_line('PRO PRO update main report4');
      put_line('SPO 00001_edb360_323688_index.html APP;');
      put_line('PRO <a href="sqlash_'||sql_rec.sql_id||'.zip">sqlash(zip)</a>');
      put_line('SPO OFF;');
      put_line('PRO PRO zip');
      put_line('HOS zip -mj edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 sqlash_'||sql_rec.sql_id||'.zip >> 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
      put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00001_edb360_323688_index.html >> 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
    END IF;
    IF sql_rec.rank_num <= 0 AND '' IS NULL THEN
      put_line('COL edb360_bypass NEW_V edb360_bypass;');
      put_line('SELECT '' echo timeout '' edb360_bypass FROM DUAL WHERE (DBMS_UTILITY.GET_TIME - :edb360_time0) / 100  >  :edb360_max_seconds;');
      update_log('SQLHC rank:'||sql_rec.rank_num||' SQL_ID:'||sql_rec.sql_id||' TOP_type:'||sql_rec.top_type);
      put_line('@@'||CHR(38)||CHR(38)||'edb360_bypass.sql/sqlhc.sql T '||sql_rec.sql_id);
      put_line('PRO PRO update main report5');
      put_line('SPO 00001_edb360_323688_index.html APP;');
      put_line('PRO <a href="'||CHR(38)||chr(38)||'files_prefix..zip">sqlhc(zip)</a>');
      put_line('SPO OFF;');
      put_line('PRO PRO zip');
      put_line('HOS zip -mj edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 '||CHR(38)||chr(38)||'files_prefix..zip >> 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
      put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00001_edb360_323688_index.html >> 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
    END IF;
    IF sql_rec.rank_num <= 8 THEN
      /* moved down into its own cursor loop (to avoid planx hanging */
      put_line('PRO PRO update main report6');
      put_line('SPO 00001_edb360_323688_index.html APP;');
      put_line('PRO <a href="sqld360_323688_'||sql_rec.sql_id||'_742967_20201106_1122.zip">sqld360(zip)</a>');
      put_line('SPO OFF;');
      put_line('PRO PRO zip');
      put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00001_edb360_323688_index.html >> 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
    END IF;
    put_line('PRO PRO update main report7');
    put_line('SPO 00001_edb360_323688_index.html APP;');
    put_line('PRO </li>');
    put_line('SPO OFF;');
    put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00001_edb360_323688_index.html >> 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
  END LOOP;
  CLOSE sql_cur;
  IF '12.1.0.2.0' >= '12' AND 'FRSTPROD' <> 'NONE' THEN
    put_line('SPO 00002_edb360_323688_log.txt APP;');
    put_line('PRO PRO ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~');
    put_line('PRO PRO changes PDB to FRSTPROD');
    put_line('ALTER SESSION SET CONTAINER = FRSTPROD;');
    put_line('PRO PRO ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~');
    put_line('SPO OFF;');
    put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00002_edb360_323688_log.txt >> 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
    put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
  END IF;
  -- SQLd360
  put_line('PRO');
  put_line('PRO PRO ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~');
  put_line('PRO PRO ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~');
  put_line('PRO');
  put_line('PRO prepares to execute sqld360');
  put_line('PRO PRO deleting content of global temporary table "plan_table" as preparation to execute sqld360');
  put_line('DELETE plan_table;');
  OPEN sql_cur;
  LOOP
    FETCH sql_cur INTO sql_rec;
    EXIT WHEN sql_cur%NOTFOUND;
    l_count := l_count + 1;
    IF sql_rec.rank_num <= 8 THEN
      update_log('SQLD360 rank:'||sql_rec.rank_num||' SQL_ID:'||sql_rec.sql_id||' TOP_type:'||sql_rec.top_type);
      put_line('PRO PRO prepares execution of sqld360');
      IF sql_rec.rank_num <= 0 THEN
        put_line('INSERT INTO plan_table (id, statement_id, operation, options, object_node, projection) SELECT '||sql_rec.rank_num||', ''SQLD360_SQLID'', '''||sql_rec.sql_id||''', ''111031'', '''||sql_rec.pdb_name||''' , ''null'' FROM DUAL WHERE (DBMS_UTILITY.GET_TIME - :edb360_time0) / 100  <  :edb360_max_seconds;');
      ELSE
        put_line('INSERT INTO plan_table (id, statement_id, operation, options, object_node, projection) SELECT '||sql_rec.rank_num||', ''SQLD360_SQLID'', '''||sql_rec.sql_id||''', ''110031'', '''||sql_rec.pdb_name||''' , ''null'' FROM DUAL WHERE (DBMS_UTILITY.GET_TIME - :edb360_time0) / 100  <  :edb360_max_seconds;');
      END IF;
    END IF;
  END LOOP;
  CLOSE sql_cur;
  IF l_count > 0 THEN
    put_line('UNDEF 1');
    put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 99930_edb360_323688_top_sql_driver.sql >> 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
    put_line('SPO 00002_edb360_323688_log.txt APP;');
    put_line('PRO PRO ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~');
    put_line('PRO PRO plan_table content before calling sqld360');
    put_line('SELECT operation||'' ''||object_node||'' ''||options||'' ''||object_node FROM plan_table WHERE statement_id = ''SQLD360_SQLID'';');
    put_line('SPO OFF;');
    put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00002_edb360_323688_log.txt >> 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
    put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
    IF '' IS NULL AND 'Y' = 'Y' THEN
      put_line('SPO 00002_edb360_323688_log.txt APP;');
      put_line('PRO PRO ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~');
      put_line('DEF;');
      put_line('PRO PRO ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~');
      put_line('PRO PRO calling eadam (ash) for top sql and peak snaps');
      put_line('COL edb360_bypass NEW_V edb360_bypass;');
      put_line('SELECT '' echo timeout '' edb360_bypass FROM DUAL WHERE (DBMS_UTILITY.GET_TIME - :edb360_time0) / 100  >  :edb360_max_seconds;');
      put_line('EXEC DBMS_APPLICATION_INFO.SET_MODULE(''edb360'',''eadam'');');
      put_line('SPO OFF;');
      put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00002_edb360_323688_log.txt >> 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
      put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
      put_line('@@sql/'||CHR(38)||CHR(38)||'edb360_bypass.edb360_7c_eadam.sql');
    END IF;
    put_line('SPO 00002_edb360_323688_log.txt APP;');
    put_line('PRO PRO ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~');
    put_line('PRO PRO seconds left on eDB360 before calling SQLd360');
    put_line('VAR edb360_secs2go NUMBER;');
    put_line('EXEC :edb360_secs2go := 0;');
    put_line('EXEC :edb360_secs2go := :edb360_max_seconds - ROUND((DBMS_UTILITY.GET_TIME - :edb360_time0) / 100);');
    put_line('PRINT :edb360_secs2go;');
    put_line('DEF edb360_secs2go = ''0'';');
    put_line('COL edb360_secs2go NEW_V edb360_secs2go FOR A8;');
    put_line('SELECT TO_CHAR(:edb360_secs2go) edb360_secs2go FROM DUAL;');
    put_line('PRO PRO calling sqld360');
    put_line('COL edb360_bypass NEW_V edb360_bypass;');
    put_line('SELECT '' echo timeout '' edb360_bypass FROM DUAL WHERE (DBMS_UTILITY.GET_TIME - :edb360_time0) / 100  >  :edb360_max_seconds;');
    put_line('EXEC DBMS_APPLICATION_INFO.SET_MODULE(''edb360'',''sqld360'');');
    put_line('SPO OFF;');
    put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00002_edb360_323688_log.txt >> 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
    put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
    -- actual execution of sql/sqld360.sql
    put_line('@@'||CHR(38)||CHR(38)||'edb360_bypass.sqld360.sql');
    IF '12.1.0.2.0' >= '12' AND 'FRSTPROD' NOT IN ('NONE', 'CDB$ROOT', 'PDB$SEED') THEN
      put_line('SPO 00002_edb360_323688_log.txt APP;');
      put_line('PRO PRO ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~');
      put_line('PRO PRO returns to original PDB');
      put_line('ALTER SESSION SET CONTAINER = FRSTPROD;');
      put_line('PRO PRO ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~');
      put_line('SPO OFF;');
      put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00002_edb360_323688_log.txt >> 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
      put_line('HOS zip -j edb360_323688_742967_20201106_1122 00004_edb360_323688_log3.txt');
    END IF;
  END IF;
END;

WITH
pm AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM gv$sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('1hd6zv2xrvp7a')
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM dba_hist_sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('1hd6zv2xrvp7a')
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pm_pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value
 UNION
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
p AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm_pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
phv_perf AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       snap_id,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('1hd6zv2xrvp7a')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       snap_id ),
phv_stats AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       MAX(avg_et_us) p100_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p99_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p97_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p95_et_us,
       MAX(avg_cpu_us) p100_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p99_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p97_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p95_cpu_us
  FROM phv_perf
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
m AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time)/SUM(executions) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time)/SUM(executions) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets)/SUM(executions)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed)/SUM(executions)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM gv$sql
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('1hd6zv2xrvp7a')
   AND executions > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
a AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions_delta) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('1hd6zv2xrvp7a')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value )
SELECT
       p.plan_hash_value,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_mem,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_mem,
       a.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_awr,
       m.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_mem,
       a.avg_rows_processed avg_row_awr,
       m.avg_rows_processed avg_row_mem,
       a.executions executions_awr,
       m.executions executions_mem,
       LEAST(NVL(m.min_cost, a.min_cost), NVL(a.min_cost, m.min_cost)) min_cost,
       GREATEST(NVL(m.max_cost, a.max_cost), NVL(a.max_cost, m.max_cost)) max_cost,
       p.nl,
       p.hj,
       p.mj,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_cpu_ms
  FROM p, m, a, phv_stats s
 WHERE p.plan_hash_value = m.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = a.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = s.plan_hash_value(+)
 ORDER BY
       NVL(a.avg_et_us, m.avg_et_us), m.avg_et_us

WITH
pm AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM gv$sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('561s98r3c15ad')
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM dba_hist_sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('561s98r3c15ad')
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pm_pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value
 UNION
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
p AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm_pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
phv_perf AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       snap_id,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('561s98r3c15ad')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       snap_id ),
phv_stats AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       MAX(avg_et_us) p100_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p99_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p97_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p95_et_us,
       MAX(avg_cpu_us) p100_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p99_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p97_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p95_cpu_us
  FROM phv_perf
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
m AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time)/SUM(executions) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time)/SUM(executions) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets)/SUM(executions)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed)/SUM(executions)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM gv$sql
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('561s98r3c15ad')
   AND executions > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
a AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions_delta) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('561s98r3c15ad')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value )
SELECT
       p.plan_hash_value,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_mem,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_mem,
       a.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_awr,
       m.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_mem,
       a.avg_rows_processed avg_row_awr,
       m.avg_rows_processed avg_row_mem,
       a.executions executions_awr,
       m.executions executions_mem,
       LEAST(NVL(m.min_cost, a.min_cost), NVL(a.min_cost, m.min_cost)) min_cost,
       GREATEST(NVL(m.max_cost, a.max_cost), NVL(a.max_cost, m.max_cost)) max_cost,
       p.nl,
       p.hj,
       p.mj,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_cpu_ms
  FROM p, m, a, phv_stats s
 WHERE p.plan_hash_value = m.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = a.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = s.plan_hash_value(+)
 ORDER BY
       NVL(a.avg_et_us, m.avg_et_us), m.avg_et_us

pm AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM gv$sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('7uxfahgurqu0d')
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM dba_hist_sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('7uxfahgurqu0d')
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pm_pa AS (

  FROM pm
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value

SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),

  FROM pm_pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
phv_perf AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       snap_id,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('7uxfahgurqu0d')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       snap_id ),
phv_stats AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       MAX(avg_et_us) p100_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p99_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p97_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p95_et_us,
       MAX(avg_cpu_us) p100_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p99_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p97_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p95_cpu_us
  FROM phv_perf
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
m AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time)/SUM(executions) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time)/SUM(executions) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets)/SUM(executions)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed)/SUM(executions)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM gv$sql
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('7uxfahgurqu0d')
   AND executions > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
a AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions_delta) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('7uxfahgurqu0d')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value )
SELECT
       p.plan_hash_value,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_mem,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_mem,
       a.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_awr,
       m.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_mem,
       a.avg_rows_processed avg_row_awr,
       m.avg_rows_processed avg_row_mem,
       a.executions executions_awr,
       m.executions executions_mem,
       LEAST(NVL(m.min_cost, a.min_cost), NVL(a.min_cost, m.min_cost)) min_cost,
       GREATEST(NVL(m.max_cost, a.max_cost), NVL(a.max_cost, m.max_cost)) max_cost,
       p.nl,
       p.hj,
       p.mj,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_cpu_ms
  FROM p, m, a, phv_stats s
 WHERE p.plan_hash_value = m.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = a.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = s.plan_hash_value(+)
 ORDER BY
       NVL(a.avg_et_us, m.avg_et_us), m.avg_et_us

  from DBA_HIST_SQLTEXT
            where SQL_ID=:v_sql_id and
               
     dbid = :dbid and nvl(con_id, 0) = nvl(:con_id, 0)

WITH
pm AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM gv$sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('d1bmu84pdu6gx')
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, operation,
       CASE operation WHEN 'NESTED LOOPS' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END nl,
       CASE operation WHEN 'HASH JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END hj,
       CASE operation WHEN 'MERGE JOIN' THEN COUNT(DISTINCT id) ELSE 0 END mj
  FROM dba_hist_sql_plan
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('d1bmu84pdu6gx')
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       operation ),
pm_pa AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value
 UNION
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
p AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value, MAX(nl) nl, MAX(hj) hj, MAX(mj) mj
  FROM pm_pa
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
phv_perf AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       snap_id,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('d1bmu84pdu6gx')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value,
       snap_id ),
phv_stats AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       MAX(avg_et_us) p100_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p99_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p97_et_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_et_us) p95_et_us,
       MAX(avg_cpu_us) p100_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.99) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p99_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.97) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p97_cpu_us,
       PERCENTILE_DISC(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY avg_cpu_us) p95_cpu_us
  FROM phv_perf
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
m AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time)/SUM(executions) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time)/SUM(executions) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets)/SUM(executions)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed)/SUM(executions)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM gv$sql
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('d1bmu84pdu6gx')
   AND executions > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value ),
a AS (
SELECT plan_hash_value,
       SUM(elapsed_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_et_us,
       SUM(cpu_time_delta)/SUM(executions_delta) avg_cpu_us,
       ROUND(SUM(buffer_gets_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_buffer_gets,
       ROUND(SUM(rows_processed_delta)/SUM(executions_delta)) avg_rows_processed,
       SUM(executions_delta) executions,
       MIN(optimizer_cost) min_cost,
       MAX(optimizer_cost) max_cost
  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat
 WHERE sql_id = TRIM('d1bmu84pdu6gx')
   AND executions_delta > 0
   AND optimizer_cost > 0
   AND :license = 'Y'
 GROUP BY
       plan_hash_value )
SELECT
       p.plan_hash_value,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_et_ms_mem,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(a.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_awr,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(m.avg_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) avg_cpu_ms_mem,
       a.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_awr,
       m.avg_buffer_gets avg_bg_mem,
       a.avg_rows_processed avg_row_awr,
       m.avg_rows_processed avg_row_mem,
       a.executions executions_awr,
       m.executions executions_mem,
       LEAST(NVL(m.min_cost, a.min_cost), NVL(a.min_cost, m.min_cost)) min_cost,
       GREATEST(NVL(m.max_cost, a.max_cost), NVL(a.max_cost, m.max_cost)) max_cost,
       p.nl,
       p.hj,
       p.mj,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_et_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_et_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p100_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p100_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p99_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p99_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p97_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p97_cpu_ms,
       LPAD(TRIM(TO_CHAR(ROUND(s.p95_cpu_us/1e3, 6), '9999,990.000')), 11) p95_cpu_ms
  FROM p, m, a, phv_stats s
 WHERE p.plan_hash_value = m.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = a.plan_hash_value(+)
   AND p.plan_hash_value = s.plan_hash_value(+)
 ORDER BY
       NVL(a.avg_et_us, m.avg_et_us), m.avg_et_us

SELECT i.table_owner||'.'||i.table_name||' '||i.owner||'.'||i.index_name table_and_index_name,
       i.partitioned,
       i.degree,
       i.index_type,
       i.uniqueness,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM dba_ind_columns ic WHERE ic.index_owner = i.owner AND ic.index_name = i.index_name) columns,
       i.status,
       i.visibility,
       i.blevel,
       i.leaf_blocks,
       i.distinct_keys,
       i.clustering_factor,
       i.num_rows,
       i.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(i.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       i.global_stats
  FROM dba_indexes i
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','CAREADMIN_LOG'),('THH_C4C','T_OTHER_INSURANCE'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'))
 ORDER BY
       i.table_owner,
       i.table_name,
       i.owner,
       i.index_name

  crgets, cugets, reads, writes, etime, 
                 mem_opt, mem_one, 
  last_mem_used, last_mem_usage, opt_cnt, 
                 one_cnt, 
  multi_cnt, max_tmp, last_tmp from (select /*+ no_merge */ 
                 
           vp.id id, vp.parent_id parent_id, vp.partition_id,
                
            vp.timestamp, vp.optimizer, vp.search_columns,
                   
         vp.depth depth, vp.position position, 
                          
  vp.operation operation, vp.options options,
                          
  vp.cost cost, vp.time time, 
                          vp.cardinality 
  cardinality, vp.bytes bytes, 
                          vp.object_node 
  object_node,
                          vp.object_name object_name, 
        
                    vp.object_owner object_owner, 
                          
  vp.object_type object_type, null as object_instance,
                       
     vp.other_tag other_tag, 
                          vp.partition_start 
  partition_start,
                          vp.partition_stop partition_stop,
   
                          vp.distribution distribution, 
                 
           vp.temp_space temp_space, vp.io_cost io_cost,
                     
       vp.cpu_cost cpu_cost, 
                          vp.filter_predicates 
  filter_predicates, 
                          vp.access_predicates 
  access_predicates, 
                          vp.other other, vp.projection 
  projection, 
                          vp.qblock_name qblock_name, 
        
                    vp.object_alias object_alias, 
                          
  vp.other_xml other_xml, 
                          v$sql.sql_profile 
  sql_profile, 
                          v$sql.sql_plan_baseline 
  sql_plan_baseline, vp.last_starts starts,
                                  
     vp.last_output_rows outrows, 
                                     
  vp.last_cr_buffer_gets crgets, 
                                     
  vp.last_cu_buffer_gets cugets, 
                                     
  vp.last_disk_reads reads,
                                     
  vp.last_disk_writes writes, 
                                     
  vp.last_elapsed_time etime,
                                     
  vp.estimated_optimal_size mem_opt,
                                     
  vp.estimated_onepass_size mem_one,
                                     
  vp.last_memory_used last_mem_used,
                                     
  vp.last_execution last_mem_usage,
                                     
  vp.optimal_executions opt_cnt,
                                     
  vp.onepass_executions one_cnt,
                                     
  vp.multipasses_executions multi_cnt,
                                     
  vp.max_tempseg_size max_tmp,
                                     
  vp.last_tempseg_size last_tmp
           from V$SQL_PLAN_STATISTICS_ALL vp, 
  v$sql where vp.SQL_ID = :1  and vp.child_number=0 and vp.SQL_ID = 
  v$sql.SQL_ID and v$sql.is_obsolete = 'N' and v$sql.address = vp.address and 
  v$sql.child_number= :2) order by id

SELECT i.table_owner||'.'||i.table_name||' '||i.owner||'.'||i.index_name table_and_index_name,
       i.partitioned,
       i.degree,
       i.index_type,
       i.uniqueness,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM dba_ind_columns ic WHERE ic.index_owner = i.owner AND ic.index_name = i.index_name) columns,
       i.status,
       i.visibility,
       i.blevel,
       i.leaf_blocks,
       i.distinct_keys,
       i.clustering_factor,
       i.num_rows,
       i.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(i.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       i.global_stats
  FROM dba_indexes i
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','T_PROVIDER_CHOICE'))
 ORDER BY
       i.table_owner,
       i.table_name,
       i.owner,
       i.index_name

SELECT i.table_owner||'.'||i.table_name||' '||i.owner||'.'||i.index_name table_and_index_name,
       i.partitioned,
       i.degree,
       i.index_type,
       i.uniqueness,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM dba_ind_columns ic WHERE ic.index_owner = i.owner AND ic.index_name = i.index_name) columns,
       i.status,
       i.visibility,
       i.blevel,
       i.leaf_blocks,
       i.distinct_keys,
       i.clustering_factor,
       i.num_rows,
       i.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(i.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       i.global_stats
  FROM dba_indexes i
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','MLOG$_T_MEMBCTCS'),('THH_C4C','T_PROVIDER_CHOICE'),('THH_C4C','T_PROVIDER_CHOICE_ROLE_XREF'))
 ORDER BY
       i.table_owner,
       i.table_name,
       i.owner,
       i.index_name

SELECT i.table_owner||'.'||i.table_name||' '||i.owner||'.'||i.index_name table_and_index_name,
       i.partitioned,
       i.degree,
       i.index_type,
       i.uniqueness,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM dba_ind_columns ic WHERE ic.index_owner = i.owner AND ic.index_name = i.index_name) columns,
       i.status,
       i.visibility,
       i.blevel,
       i.leaf_blocks,
       i.distinct_keys,
       i.clustering_factor,
       i.num_rows,
       i.sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(i.last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       i.global_stats
  FROM dba_indexes i
 WHERE (i.table_owner, i.table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','T_ENNS'))
 ORDER BY
       i.table_owner,
       i.table_name,
       i.owner,
       i.index_name

              timestamp, optimizer, position, search_columns, depth , 
  operation, options, object_name, object_owner, object_type, null as 
  object_instance, cardinality, bytes, temp_space, cost, io_cost, cpu_cost, 
  time, partition_start, partition_stop, object_node, other_tag, distribution,
   projection, access_predicates, filter_predicates, other, qblock_name, 
  object_alias, other_xml, sql_profile, sql_plan_baseline, starts, outrows, 
  crgets, cugets, reads, writes, etime, 
                 mem_opt, mem_one,

                 one_cnt,

           vp.id id, vp.parent_id parent_id, vp.partition_id,
                
            vp.timestamp, vp.optimizer, vp.search_columns,
                   
         vp.depth depth, vp.position position, 
                          
  vp.operation operation, vp.options options,

                          vp.cardinality 
  cardinality, vp.bytes bytes, 
                          vp.object_node 
  object_node,
                          vp.object_name object_name, 
        
                    vp.object_owner object_owner, 
                          
  vp.object_type object_type, null as object_instance,
                       
     vp.other_tag other_tag, 
                          vp.partition_start 
  partition_start,
                          vp.partition_stop partition_stop,
   
                          vp.distribution distribution, 
                 
           vp.temp_space temp_space, vp.io_cost io_cost,
                     
       vp.cpu_cost cpu_cost, 
                          vp.filter_predicates 
  filter_predicates, 
                          vp.access_predicates 
  access_predicates, 
                          vp.other other, vp.projection 
  projection, 
                          vp.qblock_name qblock_name, 
        
                    vp.object_alias object_alias, 
                          
  vp.other_xml other_xml, 
                          v$sql.sql_profile 
  sql_profile, 
                          v$sql.sql_plan_baseline 
  sql_plan_baseline, vp.last_starts starts,
                                  
     vp.last_output_rows outrows, 
                                     
  vp.last_cr_buffer_gets crgets, 
                                     
  vp.last_cu_buffer_gets cugets, 
                                     
  vp.last_disk_reads reads,
                                     
  vp.last_disk_writes writes, 
                                     
  vp.last_elapsed_time etime,
                                     
  vp.estimated_optimal_size mem_opt,
                                     
  vp.estimated_onepass_size mem_one,

  vp.max_tempseg_size max_tmp,
                                     
  vp.last_tempseg_size last_tmp
           from V$SQL_PLAN_STATISTICS_ALL vp, 
  v$sql where vp.SQL_ID = :1  and vp.child_number=3 and vp.SQL_ID =

SELECT owner||'.'||table_name table_name,
       partitioned,
       degree,
       temporary,
       blocks,
       num_rows,
       avg_row_len,
       sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       global_stats,
       compression
  FROM dba_tables
 WHERE (owner, table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','A_APBL'),('THH_C4C','A_APBLSRVC'),('THH_C4C','A_MEMBDGISBASE'),('THH_C4C','A_USR'),('THH_C4C','MV_PATID_CLINIC_COND_SRVCD'),('THH_C4C','T_DRUGCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCLCLM'),('THH_C4C','T_MDCT'),('THH_C4C','T_SRVC'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'))
 ORDER BY
       owner,
       table_name

SELECT /*+ opt_param('parallel_execution_enabled', 'false') */
               
          /* EXEC_FROM_DBMS_XPLAN */ id, parent_id, partition_id, 
           
              timestamp, optimizer, position, search_columns, depth , 
  operation, options, object_name, object_owner, object_type, null as 
  object_instance, cardinality, bytes, temp_space, cost, io_cost, cpu_cost, 
  time, partition_start, partition_stop, object_node, other_tag, distribution,
   projection, access_predicates, filter_predicates, other, qblock_name, 
  object_alias, other_xml, sql_profile, sql_plan_baseline, starts, outrows, 
  crgets, cugets, reads, writes, etime, 
                 mem_opt, mem_one, 
  last_mem_used, last_mem_usage, opt_cnt, 
                 one_cnt, 
  multi_cnt, max_tmp, last_tmp from (select /*+ no_merge */ 
                 
           vp.id id, vp.parent_id parent_id, vp.partition_id,
                
            vp.timestamp, vp.optimizer, vp.search_columns,
                   
         vp.depth depth, vp.position position, 
                          
  vp.operation operation, vp.options options,
                          
  vp.cost cost, vp.time time, 
                          vp.cardinality 
  cardinality, vp.bytes bytes, 
                          vp.object_node 
  object_node,
                          vp.object_name object_name, 
        
                    vp.object_owner object_owner, 
                          
  vp.object_type object_type, null as object_instance,
                       
     vp.other_tag other_tag, 
                          vp.partition_start 
  partition_start,
                          vp.partition_stop partition_stop,
   
                          vp.distribution distribution, 
                 
           vp.temp_space temp_space, vp.io_cost io_cost,
                     
       vp.cpu_cost cpu_cost, 
                          vp.filter_predicates 
  filter_predicates, 
                          vp.access_predicates 
  access_predicates, 
                          vp.other other, vp.projection 
  projection, 
                          vp.qblock_name qblock_name, 
        
                    vp.object_alias object_alias, 
                          
  vp.other_xml other_xml, 
                          v$sql.sql_profile 
  sql_profile, 
                          v$sql.sql_plan_baseline 
  sql_plan_baseline, vp.last_starts starts,
                                  
     vp.last_output_rows outrows, 
                                     
  vp.last_cr_buffer_gets crgets, 
                                     
  vp.last_cu_buffer_gets cugets, 
                                     
  vp.last_disk_reads reads,
                                     
  vp.last_disk_writes writes, 
                                     
  vp.last_elapsed_time etime,
                                     
  vp.estimated_optimal_size mem_opt,
                                     
  vp.estimated_onepass_size mem_one,
                                     
  vp.last_memory_used last_mem_used,
                                     
  vp.last_execution last_mem_usage,
                                     
  vp.optimal_executions opt_cnt,
                                     
  vp.onepass_executions one_cnt,
                                     
  vp.multipasses_executions multi_cnt,
                                     
  vp.max_tempseg_size max_tmp,
                                     
  vp.last_tempseg_size last_tmp
           from V$SQL_PLAN_STATISTICS_ALL vp, 
  v$sql where vp.SQL_ID = :1  and vp.child_number=1 and vp.SQL_ID = 
  v$sql.SQL_ID and v$sql.is_obsolete = 'N' and v$sql.address = vp.address and 
  v$sql.child_number= :2) order by id

SELECT owner||'.'||table_name table_name,
       partitioned,
       degree,
       temporary,
       blocks,
       num_rows,
       avg_row_len,
       sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       global_stats,
       compression
  FROM dba_tables
 WHERE (owner, table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','A_APBL'),('THH_C4C','A_CM_BASEBASE'),('THH_C4C','A_MEMBDGISBASE'),('THH_C4C','A_PVDRASTN'),('THH_C4C','A_UM_BASE'),('THH_C4C','A_USR'),('THH_C4C','MV_PATID_CM_COND_PROVIDER'))
 ORDER BY
       owner,
       table_name

                          vp.object_name object_name, 
        
                    vp.object_owner object_owner, 
                          
  vp.object_type object_type, null as object_instance,
                       
     vp.other_tag other_tag, 
                          vp.partition_start 
  partition_start,
                          vp.partition_stop partition_stop,
   
                          vp.distribution distribution, 
                 
           vp.temp_space temp_space, vp.io_cost io_cost,
                     
       vp.cpu_cost cpu_cost, 
                          vp.filter_predicates 
  filter_predicates, 
                          vp.access_predicates 
  access_predicates, 
                          vp.other other, vp.projection 
  projection, 
                          vp.qblock_name qblock_name, 
        
                    vp.object_alias object_alias, 
                          
  vp.other_xml other_xml, 
                          v$sql.sql_profile 
  sql_profile, 
                          v$sql.sql_plan_baseline 
  sql_plan_baseline, vp.last_starts starts,
                                  
     vp.last_output_rows outrows, 
                                     
  vp.last_cr_buffer_gets crgets, 
                                     
  vp.last_cu_buffer_gets cugets, 
                                     
  vp.last_disk_reads reads,
                                     
  vp.last_disk_writes writes, 
                                     
  vp.last_elapsed_time etime,
                                     
  vp.estimated_optimal_size mem_opt,
                                     
  vp.estimated_onepass_size mem_one,
                                     
  vp.last_memory_used last_mem_used,
                                     
  vp.last_execution last_mem_usage,
                                     
  vp.optimal_executions opt_cnt,
                                     
  vp.onepass_executions one_cnt,
                                     
  vp.multipasses_executions multi_cnt,
                                     
  vp.max_tempseg_size max_tmp,
                                     
  vp.last_tempseg_size last_tmp
           from V$SQL_PLAN_STATISTICS_ALL vp, 
  v$sql where vp.SQL_ID = :1  and vp.child_number=9 and vp.SQL_ID = 
  v$sql.SQL_ID and v$sql.is_obsolete = 'N' and v$sql.address = vp.address and 
  v$sql.child_number= :2) order by id

SELECT owner||'.'||table_name table_name,
       partitioned,
       degree,
       temporary,
       blocks,
       num_rows,
       avg_row_len,
       sample_size,
       TO_CHAR(last_analyzed, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') last_analyzed,
       global_stats,
       compression
  FROM dba_tables
 WHERE (owner, table_name) IN (('THH_C4C','CAREADMIN_LOG'),('THH_C4C','T_OTHER_INSURANCE'),('THH_C4C','T_USR'))
 ORDER BY
       owner,
       table_name
